ll%20the%20available%20routes%20to%20their%20destination%20as%20it's%20often%20cheaper%20than%20taking%20a%20direct%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDon't%20be%20afraid%20of%20stopovers.%20Flight%20pairings%20with%20a%20stopover%20are%20sometimes%20cheaper%20than%20a%20non-stop%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fskiplagging-how-to-save-money-flights-travel-airfare-airline-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708781161000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d836fd6080194819f99c9a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fskiplagging-how-to-save-money-flights-travel-airfare-airline-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Travelers%20should%20search%20for%20the%20cheapest%20airfare%20upgrades%20and%20not%20just%20the%20cheapest%20economy%20fare%2C%20Bobby%20Laurie%20told%20Business%20Insider.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mdescalsota%40insider.com%20(Marielle%20Descalsota)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20era%20of%20the%20Magnificent%207%20is%20over%2C%20says%20the%20analyst%20who%20invented%20the%20term%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221708%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20headstone%20on%20a%20laptop%20keyboard%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d8ca7090413ab8e1d66f75%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22854%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20era%20of%20the%20Magnificent%20Seven%20is%20drawing%20to%20a%20close.%3Cp%3EBrankospejs%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIt%20was%20a%20good%20run%2C%20but%20the%20era%20of%20the%20Magnificent%20Seven%20is%20over%20for%20the%20stock%20market.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20group's%20fortunes%20have%20diverged%2C%20with%20stocks%20like%20Nvidia%20soaring%20and%20Tesla%20tanking.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20see%20these%20seven%20names%20rising%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20analyst%20who%20coined%20the%20nickname%20for%20the%20group.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Magnificent%20Seven%20are%20looking%20a%20little%20less%20magnificent%2C%20and%20aren't%20really%20even%20a%20band%20of%20seven%20anymore.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20diverging%20fortunes%20this%20year%20might%20mark%20the%20end%20of%20an%20era%20for%20the%20stock%20market%2C%20according%20to%20the%20analyst%20who%20coined%20the%20nickname%20for%20the%20group%20of%20mega-cap%20giants.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20note%20titled%20%26quot%3BR.I.P%20the%20Magnificent%20Seven%20Era%2C%26quot%3B%20Mike%20O'Rourke%2C%20chief%20market%20strategist%20from%20Jones%20Trading%2C%20said%20the%20group's%20dominance%20over%20the%20stock%20market%20is%20coming%20to%20a%20close.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20in%20April%202023%2C%20when%20O'Rourke%20invented%20the%20moniker%20(although%20some%20say%20it%20was%20BofA's%20Michael%20Hartnett%20who%20coined%20the%20term)%2C%20the%20Magnificent%20Seven%20contributed%20to%20a%20stunning%2088%25%20of%20year-to-date%20gains.%20Today%2C%20that%20grip%20on%20the%20market%20has%20loosened.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20Michael%20Hartnett%20noted%20that%20the%20seven%20biggest%20stocks%20%E2%80%94%20Apple%2C%20Meta%20Platforms%2C%20Nvidia%2C%20Tesla%2C%20Amazon%2C%20and%20Microsoft%20%E2%80%94%20accounted%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Ftech-stocks-magnificent-7-dot-com-1999-bubble-inflation-recession-2024-2%5C%22%3E45%25%20of%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500's%20gains%3C%2Fa%3E.%20That's%20still%20a%20lot%2C%20but%20it's%20markedly%20less%20than%20the%20hold%20it%20once%20had.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20with%20the%20market%20rally%20broadening%20out%2C%20and%20with%20stocks%20within%20the%20Magnificent%20Seven%20embarking%20on%20different%20trajectories%20(think%20Nvidia%20versus%20Tesla)%2C%20it's%20becoming%20easier%20for%20investors%20to%20differentiate%20between%20members%20of%20the%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20big%20rising%20tide%20of%20seven%20names%20lift%5Bing%5D%20all%20boats%20in%20the%20stock%20market%2C%20is%20what%20I%20see%20ending%2C%26quot%3B%20O'Rourke%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20see%20these%20seven%20names%20rising%20together.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EDiverging%20fortunes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22raw%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2Ffhulw%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22It's%20the%20end%20of%20an%20era%20for%20the%20Magnificent%20Seven%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22450%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20one%2C%20the%20Magnificent%20Seven%20aren't%20moving%20in%20the%20same%20direction%20anymore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETake%20Nvidia%2C%20for%20example.%20The%20company%20has%20taken%20off%20on%20the%20AI%20rocket%2C%20its%20stock%20flying%20into%20the%20stratosphere%2C%20up%2066%25%20so%20far%20this%20year.%20The%20chipmaker%20posted%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-news-today-spx-nvidia-price-outlook-record-high-2024-2%5C%22%3Eblowout%20earnings%20report%20this%20week%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20swung%20the%20share%20price%20up%2016%25%20in%20a%20day%2C%20good%20for%20the%20biggest%20market-cap%20surge%20ever.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20spike%20came%20just%20weeks%20after%20Meta%20posted%20a%20similar%20record%20after%20its%20own%20earnings%20report%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fmeta-stock-price-q4-earnings-reaction-wall-street-notes-zuckerberg-2024-2%5C%22%3Eboosted%20the%20stock%2020%25%20in%20a%20day.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20moves%20are%20in%20stark%20contrast%20to%20Tesla's%20f