oesn't%20mean%20there%20is%20something%20wrong%20with%20your%20relationship%2C%20Nasir%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20you%20navigate%20this%20as%20a%20consumer%20of%20social%20media%2C%20it's%20really%20important%20to%20always%20check%20in%20with%20yourself%20and%20ask%20yourself%2C%20what%20do%20I%20really%20want%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcringe-couple-pics-social-media-relationship-health-happiness-therapist-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708777741000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d8ba12ce7f1785b2e36ec3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcringe-couple-pics-social-media-relationship-health-happiness-therapist-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22From%20Taylor%20and%20Travis%20to%20Selena%20and%20Benny%2C%20cringe%20couples%20are%20shouting%20about%20their%20love%20from%20the%20rooftops.%20Therapists%20explain%20why%20that%20might%20be.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kschewitz%40businessinsider.com%20(Kim%20Schewitz)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcringe-couple-pics-social-media-relationship-health-happiness-therapist-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20got%20my%20son%20a%20pocket%20knife%20instead%20of%20a%20cellphone.%20Here's%20why.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kids%20building%20a%20fort%20in%20the%20woods%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cf73f66fcb546d2d50977d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author's%20son%20spends%20time%20in%20the%20woods%20with%20his%20friends%20building%20structures%20and%20getting%20dirty.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffi