20that's%20not%20trying%20to%20sell%20an%20infinite%20amount%20of%20units%2C%26quot%3B%20Siegel%20said%20about%20the%20luxury%20sector.%20%26quot%3BCreating%20another%20handbag%20would%20be%20easy%2C%20and%20selling%20it%20would%20be%20even%20easier%2C%20but%20realizing%20that%20would%20be%20the%20wrong%20decision%20for%20the%20brand%20is%20a%20very%20impressive%20discipline%20that%20the%20most%20successful%20luxury%20brands%20have%20internalized.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20famous%20Birkin%20bag%20epitomizes%20Herm%C3%A8s'%20approach%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjane-birkin-bag-status-symbol-best-luxury-investments-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Birkin%20is%20more%20than%20a%20trendy%20accessory%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Since%20soon%20after%20it%20was%20introduced%20in%201984%2C%20the%20bag%20%E2%80%94%20which%20has%20a%20starting%20price%20of%20around%20%2410%2C000%20but%20can%20run%20into%20the%20six%20figures%20%E2%80%94%20has%20been%20among%20the%20most%20covetable%20purses%20of%20the%20ultrarich.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228640%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Birkin%20bag%2C%20Hermes%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d8ec9f90413ab8e1d68142%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225760%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Birkin%20bag%20is%20arguably%20Herm%C3%A8s'%20most%20exclusive%20handbag%2C%20costing%20at%20least%20%2410%2C000%20%E2%80%94%20sometimes%20much%20more%20%E2%80%94%20and%20racking%20up%20yearslong%20waitlists.%3Cp%3EEdward%20Berthelot%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20something%20one%20can%20purchase%20at%20a%20department%20store%2C%20walk%20in%20off%20the%20street%20and%20buy%20at%20a%20boutique%2C%20or%20order%20online%2C%20and%20specific%20styles%20sometimes%20rack%20up%20yearslong%20waitlists.%20To%20buy%20directly%20from%20Herm%C3%A8s%2C%20customers%20must%20cultivate%20a%20history%20with%20the%20brand.%20While%20there's%20no%20steadfast%20rule%2C%20experts%20say%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fhow-to-buy-a-birkin-bag%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewannabe%20Birkin%20owners%20must%20shop%20loyally%20at%20Herm%C3%A8s%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20years%20%E2%80%94%20and%20some%20say%20spend%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20%E2%80%94%20before%20they%20get%20the%20opportunity%20to%20spend%20another%20five%20figures%20or%20more%20on%20the%20bag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20its%20iconic%20scarves%2C%20each%20made-by-hand%20item%20is%20part%20of%20a%20numbered%2C%20limited%20edition%2C%20meaning%20baked-in%20exclusivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20literally%20economics%20101%2C%26quot%3B%20retail%20industry%20expert%20and%20consultant%20Hitha%20Herzog%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20have%20short%20supply%20and%20high%2C%20high%20demand%20and%20the%20branding%20that%20goes%20with%20it%20%E2%80%94%20that%20is%20what%20fuels%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20desire%20what%20they%20can't%20easily%20obtain%2C%26quot%3B%20Nicole%20Pollard%20Bayme%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20luxury%20styling%20firm%20Lalaluxe%2C%20told%20BI%20over%20email.%20%26quot%3BCrafting%20a%20playbook%20for%20marketing%20to%20the%20luxury%20consumer%2C%20Herm%C3%A8s%20sets%20the%20standard.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHerm%C3%A8s'%20limited%20products%20only%20add%20to%20the%20appeal%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20brand%20is%20also%20consistent%20in%20its%20dedication%20to%20core%20products.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EWhile%20unafraid%20of%20whimsical%20design%2C%20the%20Birkin%20and%20Kelly%20bags%20%E2%80%94%20two%20handbags%20that%20don't%20look%20all%20that%20different%20from%20Herm%C3%A8s'%20original%20saddle%20bags%20%E2%80%94%20and%20scarves%20remain%20dependable.%20Herm%C3%A8s'%20leather%20and%20silk%20products%20account%20for%2041%25%20and%207%25%20of%20its%20revenue%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20luxury%20houses%2C%20like%20Versace%2C%20owned%20by%20Capri%20Holdings%2C%20and%20Kering's%20Balenciaga%2C%20have%20been%20built%20more%20broadly%20around%20fashion%20and%20have%20taken%20a%20more%20mass-market%20approach%2C%20partnering%20with%20different%20brands%20and%20selling%20everything%20from%20socks%20to%20blue%20jeans.%20This%20leaves%20them%20vulnerable%20to%20the%20cyclical%20nature%20of%20fashion%20%E2%80%94%20which%20Herm%C3%A8s%20has%20resisted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBrand%20equity%20is%20much%20more%20diluted%20than%20Herm%C3%A8s'%2C%26quot%3B%20Herzog%20said%20of%20brands%20like%20Gucci%20and%20Louis%20Vuitton.%20Herm%C3%A8s%20doesn't%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20%26quot%3Bancillary%20products%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20is%20%26quot%3Bvery%20different%20than%20Gucci%2C%20which%20has%20shoes%2C%20socks%2C%20sweaters%2C%20perfume%2C%20makeup%2C%20a%20deal%20with%20North%20Face.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHerm%C3%A8s%20is%20'fairly%20recession-proof'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKeeping%20it%20simple%20has%20helped%20Herm%C3%A8s%20hold%20its%20own%20as%20luxury%20brands%20start%20to%20lose%20their%20shine%20after%20a%20multiyear%20spending%20boom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20brands%20like%20Gucci%20and%20Saint%20Laurent%20have%20more%20recently%20seen%20waning%20sales%20after%20a%20prior%20boost%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flvmh-says-the-aspirational-customer-is-suffering-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Baspirational%26quot%3B%20luxury%20shoppers%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20younger%2C%20less%20affluent%20customers%20who%20flocked%20to%20these%20brands%20during%20the%20retail%20bubble%20of%20the%20past%20few%20years%20%E2%80%94%20Herm%C3%A8s's%20scarcity%20meant%20it%20was%20never%20for%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethose%20shoppers%20to%20begin%20with.%20So%2C%20there%20aren't%20as%20many%20to%20lose%20at%20a%20time%20of%20recession%20worries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBeing%20at%20the%20top%20of%20consumer%20desirability%20means%20Herm%C3%A8s%20will%20be%20the%20last%20brand%20consumers%20will%20give%20up.%20Hence%20its%20resilience%2C%26quot%3B%20Bernstein%20analyst%20Luca%20Solca%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20while%20brands%20like%20Chanel%20and%20Louis%20Vuitton%20have%20been%20criticized%20for%20what%20consumers%20consider%20unfair%20price%20hikes%2C%20Herm%C3%A8s%20%26quot%3Bhad%20been%20very%20prudent%20increasing%20prices%26quot%3B%20from%202020%20to%202022%2C%20Solca%20said.%20Between%20that%20and%20the%20company's%20attention%20to%20craftsmanship%2C%20the%20wealthy%20don't%20feel%20like%20they%20are%20being%20taken%20advantage%20of%20when%20inflation%20does%20cause%20price%20increases.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20fairly%20recession-proof%20because%20its%20key%20market%20audience%20that%20buys%20at%20the%20top%20end%20don't%20ride%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fwhiskey-rolexes-trading-cards-collectibles-federal-reserve-stock-market-outlook-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20waves%20of%20recessions%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20Winston%20Chesterfield%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Barton%2C%20a%20London%20consulting%20firm%20focused%20on%20the%20wealthy%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFrom%20the%20US%20to%20China%2C%20Herm%C3%A8s%20is%20expanding%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Herm%C3%A8s%20is%20growing.%20Last%20year%2C%20it%20opened%20two%20factories%20in%20France%3A%20one%20in%20Louviers%2C%20which%20will%20focus%20on%20the%20Kelly%20bag%2C%20and%20one%20in%20the%20Ardennes%20region.%20It%20also%20announced%20it%20will%20expand%20the%20Saint%20Junien%20facility%20in%20New%20Aquitaine%20(also%20France)%20which%20makes%20Kelly%20and%20Birkin%20bags.%20Plus%2C%20it%20opened%20storefronts%20in%20Aspen%2C%20Colorado%3B%20Naples%2C%20Florida%3B%20and%20Nanjing%2C%20China%2C%20and%20has%20one%20coming%20to%20Princeton%2C%20New%20Jersey%2C%20later%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20raised%20concerns%20among%20some%20who've%20seen%20what%20happens%20if%20brands%20expand%20too%20fast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20taking%20a%20really%20big%20step%20now%2C%20and%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20people%20might%20think%20it's%20risky%20because%20they%20are%20growing%20really%20fast%2C%26quot%3B%20Herzog%20said%2C%20pointing%20to%20the%202022%20opening%20of%20a%20boutique%20in%20Williamsburg%2C%20Brooklyn%20%E2%80%94%20not%20usually%20seen%20as%20a%20luxury%20destination.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHerm%C3%A8s%20also%20added%20more%20SKUs.%20In%20the%20beauty%20category%2C%20for%20example%2C%20it%20added%20eye%20palettes%2C%20mascara%2C%20and%20new%20lip%20colors%2C%20which%20are%20available%20at%20accessible%20prices%20compared%20to%20its%20other%20products.%20It%20has%20also%20announced%20a%20plan%20for%20a%20skincare%20line%2C%20and%20touted%20its%20new%20Maximors%20and%20Ar%C3%A7on%20bags%20in%20its%20annual%20earnings%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20all%20of%20the%20above%20helped%20the%20company%20achieve%20revenue%20growth%20of%2021%25%20last%20year%2C%20it%20raises%20questions%20about%20losing%20the%20discipline%20that%20has%20made%20the%20brand%20so%20successful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHerm%C3%A8s'%20family%20leadership%20may%20keep%20a%20tight%20leash%20on%20growth%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20major%20factor%20that%20points%20to%20no%20change%3A%20The%20company's%20sixth-generation%20leaders%20%E2%80%94%20cousins%20Axel%20and%20Pierre-Alexis%20Dumas%20%E2%80%94%20who%20have%20been%20emphatic%20about%20maintaining%20a%20commitment%20to%20quality%20and%20brand%20equity.%20In%20fact%2C%20they%20were%20pivotal%20in%20defending%20against%20a%20takeover%20by%20Bernard%20Arnault's%20LVMH%20%E2%80%94%20which%20would%20have%20made%20them%20very%2C%20very%20rich.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Dumas%20family%20basically%20have%20just%20behaved%20as%20you%20expect%20them%20to%20behave%2C%20which%20is%20they%20control%20the%20ship%20and%20they%20maintain%20standards%2C%26quot%3B%20Barton's%20Chesterfield%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey've%20never%20gone%20after%20volume.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Veronique%20Nichanlan%2C%20Axel%20Dumas%2C%20Robert%20Chavez%2C%20Pierre-Alexis%20Dumas%20and%20Henri-Louis%20Bauer%20attend%20Hermes%20Beverly%20Hills%20boutique%20opening%20on%20September%203%2C%202013%20in%20Beverly%20Hills%2C%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d8ede190413ab8e1d681c9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECousins%20Axel%20Dumas%20(third%20from%20left)%20and%20Pierre-Alexis%20Dumas%20(third%20from%20right)%20are%20the%20sixth%20generation%20to%20lead%20Herm%C3%A8s.%3Cp%3ERodrigo%20Vaz%2FFilmMagic%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20every%20generation%20before%20them%20(they%20are%20the%20great-great-great%20grandsons%20of%20founder%20Thierry%20Herm%C3%A8s)%2C%20the%20Dumas%20cousins%20apprenticed%20in%20Herm%C3%A8s'%20atelier%2C%20learning%20the%20brand's%20signature%20saddle%20stitch%20and%20how%20to%20craft%20its%20most%20covetable%20items%20as%20they%20are%20still%20made%20today%20%E2%80%94%20by%20hand.%20For%20decades%20the%20cousins%20have%20resisted%20outsourcing%2C%20manufacturing%20techniques%2C%20and%20inexpensive%20materials%20that%20would%20boost%20profits%20but%20cheapen%20the%20goods.%20Instead%2C%20they've%20invested%20in%20growing%20the%20number%20of%20craftsmen%2C%20adding%20hundreds%20each%20year%2C%20opening%20schools%20and%20training%20centers%20to%20teach%20the%20art%20of%20stitching%20and%20how%20to%20screen%20print.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20unlikely%20their%20stance%20would%20change%20now.%20Even%20the%20language%20around%20expansions%20%E2%80%94%20the%20company%20says%20it's%20opening%20workshops%2C%20not%20factories%20%E2%80%94%20points%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20its%20bags%2C%20scarves%2C%20and%20gloves%20will%20still%20be%20made%20by%20hand%20by%20Herm%C3%A8s%20artisans.%20With%20its%20current%20team%20of%20more%20than%207%2C000%20craftsmen%2C%20there's%20still%20a%20hard%20and%20fast%20limit%20on%20how%20many%20Birkins%2C%20Kellys%2C%20and%20more%20can%20be%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20going%20to%20see%20Birkins%20manufactured%20at%20the%20rate%20of%20Coach.%20That's%20never%20going%20to%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20consultant%20Herzog%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20an%20element%20of%20scarcity%20that%20they%20will%20always%20have.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20it%20is%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Eexpanding%20into%20more%20affordable%20categories%2C%20those%20aren't%20its%20bread%20and%20butter.%20Beauty%2C%20for%20example%2C%20only%20makes%20up%203.6%25%20of%20its%20revenue.%20So%20you%20may%20be%20able%20to%20afford%20a%20Herm%C3%A8s%20lip%20gloss%20%E2%80%94%20as%20many%20customers%20have%20always%20been%20able%20to%20afford%20a%20key%20chain%20or%20coin%20purse%20%E2%80%94%20but%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20you're%20getting%20anywhere%20near%20a%20Birkin%20or%20a%20Kelly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Herzog%20put%20it%3A%20%26quot%3BGo%20into%20Herm%C3%A8s%20today%20and%20say%2C%20I'd%20like%20to%20see%20a%20Birkin.%20See%20what%20happens.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20unless%20you%20are%20part%20of%20a%20very%20select%20group%2C%20expect%20to%20be%20mortified.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhermes-became-ultimate-status-symbol-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708776901000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d8ec9f90413ab8e1d68142%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhermes-became-ultimate-status-symbol-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Herm%C3%A8s'%20success%20strategy%20involves%20embracing%20scarcity%2C%20maintaining%20quality%2C%20and%20resisting%20the%20mass-market%20approach%20in%20the