%2Fadani-hints-at-collaborations-with-uber-after-meeting-ceo-khosrowshahi-124022400481_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Lt%20Governor%20Writes%20To%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20Questions%20%26quot%3BStalling%20Of%20Budget%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOpening%20another%20front%20in%20his%20battle%20with%20the%20AAP%2C%20the%20Delhi%20lieutenant%20governor%20has%20written%20to%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20and%20questioned%20the%20delay%20in%20presenting%20the%20budget.%20Hitting%20out%20at%20the%20government%2C%20LG%20VK%20Saxena%20has%20accused%20it%20of%20%26quot%3Bstalling%20the%20budget%20for%20no%20apparent%20reason%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20the%20people%20have%20a%20right%20to%20know%20how%20public%20funds%20are%20being%20used.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaturday's%20letter%20by%20the%20LG%20comes%20a%20day%20after%20his%20missive%20to%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20regarding%20five%20Comptroller%20and%20Auditor%20General%20reports%20that%2C%20he%20said%2C%20have%20been%20%26quot%3Bpending%26quot%3B%20with%20Delhi%20Finance%20Minister%20Atishi%20since%20August%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2015%2C%20the%20budget%20session%20of%20the%20Assembly%20had%20been%20extended%20till%20the%20first%20week%20of%20March%20after%20Ms%20Atishi%20had%20said%20in%20the%20House%20that%20there%20had%20been%20some%20delays%20in%20the%20finalisation%20of%20the%20financial%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Saturday's%20letter%2C%20Mr%20Saxena%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20constrained%20to%20bring%20to%20your%20notice%20that%20despite%20the%20Annual%20Financial%20Statement%20being%20ready%20and%20available%20with%20the%20Government%2C%20after%20due%20clearance%20of%20Government%20of%20India%2C%20since%20as%20long%20as%2019.02.2024%2C%20it%20is%20yet%20to%20reach%20me%20for%20causing%20it%20to%20be%20laid%20in%20the%20House%20as%20per%20law%20established.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPointing%20out%20that%20the%20Centre%20had%20approved%20the%20budget%20on%20Februar