20pandemonium%20around%20them%20as%20Arbab%20and%20his%20parents%20do.%20Yet%2C%20there%20is%20a%20profound%20universality%20in%20their%20story%20that%20is%20hard%20to%20dismiss.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20film%2C%20Ahmad%20uses%20two%20voices%20when%20he%20talks%20about%20himself%20or%20his%20feelings%20%E2%80%93%20first%20and%20third%20person.%20When%20he%20uses%20the%20latter%2C%20he%20refers%20to%20himself%20by%20name%2C%20as%20if%20in%20an%20out-of-body%20experience.%20One%20may%20see%20this%20astral%20projection%20as%20a%20metaphor%20for%20the%20Muslim%20self%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20India%20that%20often%20finds%20itself%20questioning%20its%20own%20identity%2C%20choices%20and%20ideologies%20from%20a%20distance.%20This%20internal%20fracturing%20of%20the%20Muslim%20self%20is%20perhaps%20one%20of%20the%20most%20severe%20repercussions%20of%20the%20majoritarian%20onslaught%20that%20the%20community%20is%20being%20subjected%20to%20in%20India%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EInsides%20and%20Outsides%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20able%20to%20effortlessly%20oscillate%20between%20the%20home%20and%20the%20world%2C%20the%20mundane%20and%20the%20extraordinary%2C%20precisely%20because%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20pretend%20to%20be%20something%20it%20isn%E2%80%99t%20%E2%80%93%20a%20grand%20ideological%20treatise%20about%20%3Cem%3EMuslim-ness%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20a%20Hindu%20majoritarian%20India.%20So%2C%20it%20is%20able%20to%20uncompromisingly%20talk%20about%20the%20politics%20of%20majoritarian%20violence%20in%20the%20country%20and%20the%20nonchalance%20of%20daily%20life%20in%20a%20middle-class%20Muslim%20household%20at%20the%20same%20time.%20The%20political%20and%20the%20personal%20melt%20into%20each%20other%20without%20one%20completely%20diluting%20the%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20key%20motif%20in%20Ahmad%E2%80%99s%20story%20is%3A%20movement.%20He%20consciously%20dwells%20on%20it%20through%20the%20film%20using%20the%20dual%20pivots%20of%20space%20and%20time.%20Muslims%20in%20India%20have%20always%20been%20on%20the%20move%20since%20the%20Partition.%20They%20continue%20to%20be%20so%20even%20today%20%E2%80%93%20not%20because%20they%20want%20to%2C%20but%20because%20they%20are%20forced%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhmad%20himself%20is%20moving%20houses%2C%20as%20his%20father%20retires%20from%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%2C%20Delhi%20after%2065%20years%20in%20service%20as%20a%20professor.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20has%20arrived%2C%20bringing%20along%20even%20more%20uncertainty%2C%20worry%20and%20prejudice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEverything%20is%20restive%2C%20nothing%20is%20the%20same%20anymore%20%E2%80%93%20from%20their%20house%20to%20the%20world%20around%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20perhaps%2C%20the%20strongest%20motif%20in%20%3Cem%3EInsides%20and%20Outsides%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%3A%20resilience.%20Ahmad%E2%80%99s%20mother%20talks%20about%20sectarian%20violence%2C%20freedom%20of%20expression%20and%20the%20steady%20unravelling%20of%20the%20culture%20of%20respect%20while%20cooking%20biryani%20and%20admonishing%20her%20husband%20for%20driving%20too%20fast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20frame%2C%20his%20father%20directs%20his%20son%20to%20move%20the%20camera%20away%20from%20him%20and%20instead%2C%20film%20the%20posing%20peacock%20in%20the%20lawn%2C%20and%20in%20the%20next%20frame%2C%20he%20is%20seen%20shuffling%20through%20old%20files%20to%20ascertain%20which%20of%20his%20documents%20would%20stand%20the%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%E2%80%99%20(NRC)%20test.%20The%20contradictions%20chill%20the%20spine%2C%20but%20their%20infectious%20smiles%2C%20visible%20in%20nearly%20every%20frame%2C%20warm%20the%20heart.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhmad%E2%80%99s%20ability%20to%20seamlessly%20merge%20images%20and%20sounds%20is%20conspicuous%20throughout%20the%20film.%20In%20one%20scene%2C%20he%20is%20seen%20reading%20out%20the%20case%20details%20of%20various%20Muslim%20individuals%20who%20were%20lynched%20by%20Hindu%20mobs%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years%20for%20allegedly%20carrying%20beef%20or%20the%20COVID-19%20pathogen.%20As%20he%20does%20that%2C%20Ahmad%E2%80%99s%20mother%20knocks%20at%20the%20door%20and%20calls%20him%20out%20%E2%80%93%20the%20din%20growing%20louder%20and%20more%20frantic%20by%20the%20second.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fzeherkhurani-nirmala-bhuradias-latest-novel-holds-mirror-to-our-times-consumed-by-hate%5C%22%3EZeherkhurani%E2%80%99%3A%20Nirmala%20Bhuradia%E2%80%99s%20Latest%20Novel%20Holds%20a%20Mirror%20to%20Our%20Times%20Consumed%20by%20Hate%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20juxtaposition%20of%20his%20factual%20recitation%20and%20his%20mother%E2%80%99s%20desperate%20knocks%20ends%20up%20creating%20a%20harrowing%20sense%20of%20anxiety%20and%20claustrophobia.%20It%20is%20as%20if%20the%20walls%20around%20Ahmad%20were%20rapidly%20closing%20in%20on%20him.%20In%20doing%20so%2C%20he%20ends%20up%20conjuring%20a%20profound%20audio-visual%20metaphor%20for%20the%20plight%20of%20an%20average%20Indian%20Muslim%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhmad%20is%20also%20sharply%20aware%20of%20his%20own%20class%20privileges%20as%20a%20Muslim%20born%20into%20a%20well-off%20family%2C%20protected%20by%20a%20certain%20degree%20of%20generational%20security.%20He%20understands%20that%20Muslims%20from%20economically%20marginalised%20backgrounds%20face%20greater%20risks%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20India%20%E2%80%93%20a%20point%20that%20becomes%20clear%20when%20he%20explains%20to%20his%20mother%2C%20as%20they%20stand%20on%20a%20foot%20over%20bridge%20atop%20the%20erstwhile%20protest%20site%20at%20Shaheen%20Bagh%2C%20why%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20interview%20some%20of%20the%20locals%20on%20camera.%20Shaheen%20Bagh%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20is%20yet%20another%20recurring%20motif%20in%20the%20film%2C%20both%20as%20a%20Muslim%20ghetto%20and%20a%20site%20of%20righteous%20resistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EInsides%20and%20Outsides%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20not%20an%20ideological%20manifesto.%20It%20is%2C%20rather%2C%20a%20deeply%20personal%20diary%20of%20a%20pensive%2C%20perplexed%20and%20perturbed%20self%20that%20today%20finds%20itself%20dangling%20between%20two%20different%20worlds%3B%20a%20collection%2C%20even%2C%20of%20intimate%20thoughts%20jotted%20hurriedly%20on%20small%20pieces%20of%20paper%3B%20as%20assortment%20of%2C%20as%20Ahmad%20himself%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9Cdrafts%20on%20moving%E2%80%9D.%20Yet%2C%20it%20is%20also%20a%20tender%20story%20of%20bearing%20witness%20to%20political%20tumult%2C%20and%20of%20seeking%20refuge%20in%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20must%20thank%20Ahmad%20for%20letting%20us%20bear%20witness%20alongside%20him%2C%20for%20generously%20opening%20the%20doors%20of%20his%20home%20for%20us%2C%20and%20for%20telling%20a%20story%20that%20needed%20to%20be%20told.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAngshuman%20Choudhury%20is%20an%20associate%20fellow%20at%20the%20Centre%20for%20Policy%20Research%2C%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708776052000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F24135539%2FScreen-Shot-2024-02-24-at-1.55.04-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Finsides-and-outsides-arbab-ahmads-documentary-is-a-tender-tale-of-bearing-witness%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20the%20title%20suggests%2C%20'Insides%20and%20Outsides'%20is%20about%20two%20worlds%3A%20the%20household%20and%20the%20country%3B%20the%20family%20and%20the%20society.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Finsides-and-outsides-arbab-ahmads-documentary-is-a-tender-tale-of-bearing-witness%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20catapulted%20off%20the%20deck%20of%20a%20US%20aircraft%20carrier%20in%20a%20largely%20windowless%20prop%20plane%20the%20Navy's%20been%20flying%20