0a%20full%20stop%20in%20just%20three%20seconds.%20It%20was%20violent%20and%20unlike%20anything%20I'd%20ever%20experienced%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20was%20still%20less%20intense%20than%20taking%20off%20from%20the%20Eisenhower%20the%20next%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22My%20first%20look%20at%20the%20flight%20deck%20after%20landing%20on%20the%20USS%20Dwight%20D.%20Eisenhower.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d773a3f533b039a885faaa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20first%20look%20at%20the%20flight%20deck%20after%20landing%20on%20the%20USS%20Dwight%20D.%20Eisenhower.%3Cp%3EJake%20Epstein%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20our%20return%20flight%2C%20we%20watched%20a%20brief%20safety%20video%20and%20were%20given%20the%20same%20gear%20as%20our%20inbound%20flight%20%E2%80%94%20then%20told%20right%20away%20to%20put%20on%20our%20goggles.%20Boarding%20the%20Greyhound%2C%20I%20grabbed%20a%20seat%20that%20had%20something%20of%20a%20window%20view%2C%20with%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20stretch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20quick%20taxi%2C%20we%20were%20in%20position%20to%20take%20off.%20Because%20the%20Ike's%20runways%20are%20so%20short%2C%20planes%20are%20launched%20from%20a%20catapult%2C%20which%20is%20a%20steam-powered%20mechanism%20that%20slingshots%20the%20aircraft%20forward%20at%20a%20fast%20speed.%20I%20was%20dreading%20this.%20(I'm%20not%20a%20big%20fan%20of%20roller%20coasters%20and%20probably%20wasn't%20cut%20out%20for%20naval%20aviation).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20the%20launch%20came%2C%20and%20the%20aircraft%20shot%20forward%20incredibly%20fast%20and%20flew%20right%20off%20the%20deck%20as%20the%20force%20of%20the%20experience%20pushed%20me%20into%20my%20harness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20over%20in%20seconds%2C%20and%20I%20breathed%20a%20sigh%20of%20relief.%20But%20after%20a%20few%20minutes%2C%20I%20craned%20my%20neck%20to%20see%20out%20the%20window%20and%20noticed%20something%20odd%3A%20we%20were%20still%20at%20a%20pretty%20low%20altitude%20over%20the%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Exiting%20the%20Greyhound%20in%20Bahrain.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d7a0cece7f1785b2e333c5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EExiting%20the%20Greyhound%20in%20Bahrain.%3Cp%3EJake%20Epstein%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESuddenly%2C%20we%20shot%20up%20at%20a%20force%20that%20felt%20far%20greater%20than%20the%20catapult%20launch%2C%20gaining%20a%20lot%20of%20altitude%20in%20a%20quick%20spurt.%20I%20had%20no%20idea%20this%20was%20coming%2C%20so%20I%20grabbed%20the%20seat%20in%20front%20of%20me%20and%20closed%20my%20eyes.%20Then%2C%20in%20another%20twist%2C%20the%20aircraft%20dipped%20down%20before%20finally%20leveling%20out%20above%20the%20clouds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELaunching%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-navy-aircraft-carrier-eisenhower-planes-in-air-constantly-houthis-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20deck%20of%20an%20aircraft%20carrier%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20much%20like%20landing%20on%20one%2C%20is%20strange%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I%20can%20only%20imagine%20what%20it's%20like%20for%20naval%20aviators%20rocketing%20off%20the%20ship%20on%20a%20regular%20basis%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it%20was%20nonetheless%20an%20incredible%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20shaken%20by%20bits%20of%20turbulence%20as%20we%20flew%20back%20to%20Bahrain.%20It%20was%20a%20good%20thing%20I%20could%20see%20out%20the%20window%20because%20the%20sunset%20was%20spectacular%20that%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcatapulting-off-us-navy-aircraft-carrier-cod-greyhound-flight-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20