invasion%20of%20Ukraine%2C%20the%20embattled%20nation%20needs%20its%20friends%20more%20than%20ever.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia%20celebrated%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-troops-pull-out-key-eastern-town-avdiivka-russia-2024-2%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20landmark%20victory%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20it%20captured%20the%20eastern%20town%20of%20Avdiivka%20last%20week%2C%20and%20it%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraines-ammo-problems-hinder-ability-fire-at-russian-targets-2024-2%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erunning%20low%20on%20artillery%20ammunition.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Meanwhile%2C%20a%20%2460%20billion%20military%20aid%20package%20is%20snarled%20up%20in%20Congress%20due%20to%20opposition%20from%20some%20Republican%20Party%20lawmakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Howard%20Buffett%2C%20the%20elder%20son%20of%20Warren%2C%20the%20billionaire%20investor%20and%20Berkshire%20Hathaway%20CEO%2C%20has%20no%20intention%20of%20foresaking%20Ukraine%20or%20its%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20wartime%20leader%20and%20American%20philanthropist%20have%20a%20profound%20mutual%20respect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuffett%20told%20Business%20Insider%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20very%20few%20people%20in%20the%20world%20that%20could%20step%20up%26quot%3B%20and%20do%20what%20Zelenskyy's%20done.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20he's%20a%20pretty%20amazing%20guy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20Buffett's%20Howard%20G.%20Buffett%20Foundation%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20stalwart%20ally%20to%20Ukraine%20since%20Russia's%20full-scale%20invasion%2C%20injecting%20%24521%2C779%2C225%20into%20humanitarian%20assistance%20for%20Ukraine%20as%20of%20January%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20US%20and%20its%20'Ukraine%20fatigue'%20problem%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20guy's%20got%20to%20be%20worn%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20Buffett%20said%20of%20Zelenskyy.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20when%20he%20sleeps.%20He%20just%20is%20constantly%20going.%20He's%20been%20through%20two%20years%20of%20war%2C%20which%20is%20a%20living%20hell%2C%20and%20he's%20dealing%20with%20it%20every%20single%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20got%20to%20deal%20with%20each%20ministry%20and%20keep%20them%20focused.%20He's%20got%20to%20keep%20the%20economy%20working.%20He's%20got%20to%20be%20engaged%20on%20the%20military%20side.%20So%20to%20me%2C%20he's%20somebody%20who%20has%20stepped%20up%20and%20done%20a%20job%20that%20I%20think%20very%20few%20people%20could%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Buffett.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20anybody%20could%20have%20done%20a%20better%20job%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20observing%20that%20%26quot%3Bit's%20an%20incredible%20force%20that%20he's%20up%20against.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Buffett%20worries%20about%20Zelenskyy's%20exhausting%20schedule%20and%20sleepless%20nights%2C%20he%20is%20also%20concerned%20about%20%26quot%3BUkraine%20fatigue%26quot%3B%20effecting%20its%20most%20important%20ally%2C%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20warned%20against%20it%20last%20year%20and%20continues%20stressing%20the%20importance%20of%20supporting%20the%20war%20effort.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20lose%20interest%20over%20time%2C%20so%20keeping%20this%20going%20is%20tough.%20And%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20mistakes%20that%20the%20United%20States%20makes%20historically%20if%20we%20don't%20continue%20to%20support%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20most%20frustrating%20part%20is%20to%20watch%20the%20narrative%20in%20the%20US%20because%20you%20have%20congressmen%20and%20senators%20whose%20constituencies%20or%20districts%20are%20benefiting%20from%20this%20war%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPutting%20his%20money%20where%20his%20mouth%20is%2C%20Buffett%20said%20another%20%24300%20million%20is%20budgeted%20for%20Ukraine%20this%20year%2C%20and%20for%20the%20last%20two%20years%2C%20the%20foundation%20exceeded%20the%20budgeted%20number.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20foundation%20is%20largely%20funded%20by%20his%20father%2C%20Warren%20Buffett's%20contributions.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fbillionaires%2F%3Fembedded-checkout%3Dtrue%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWarren%20Buffett%20is%20the%20seventh%20richest%20person%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20world%2C%20boasting%20a%20net%20worth%20of%20%24138%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E'You%20have%20to%20step%20up%20big'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20December%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.president.gov.ua%2Fen%2Fnews%2Fvolodimir-zelenskij-i-govard-baffet-vidkrili-na-aleyi-smiliv-87821%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EZelenskyy%20and%20Howard%20Buffett%20visited%20a%20Kyiv%20plaza%3C%2Fa%3E%20adorned%20with%20plaques%20honoring%20Ukraine's%20most%20steadfast%20supporters%20during%20Russia's%20full-scale%20invasion%20to%20show%20the%20US%20philanthropist%20that%20his%20name%20is%20also%20etched%20on%20the%20%26quot%3BWalk%20of%20the%20Brave.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZelenskyy%20told%20Buffett%3A%20%26quot%3BYou%20are%20among%20these%20world%20leaders%20%E2%80%94%20friends%20of%20Ukraine.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuffett%20calls%20the%20war%20the%20%26quot%3Blargest%20humanitarian%20crisis%26quot%3B%20that%20he's%20witnessed%20in%20his%20lifetime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cars%20pass%20by%20destroyed%20Russian%20tanks%20beside%20a%20road%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b7993aac2de4f17ee55b20%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221282%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECars%20pass%20by%20destroyed%20Russian%20tanks%20close%20to%20Kyiv%2C%20Ukraine%2C%20in%20May%202022.%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FEfrem%20Lukatsky%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20Russia%20invaded%20Ukraine%20in%202022%2C%20I%20felt%20like%20it%20was%20one%20of%20those%20situations%20where%20you%20have%20to%20step%20up%20right%20away%2C%20and%20you%20have%20to%20step%20up%20big.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20foundation%20focuses%20on%20conflict%20mitigation%20and%20food%20security%2C%20issues%20that%20converge%20in%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20end%20of%202024%2C%20the%20foundation%20will%20give%20Ukraine%20at%20least%20%24800%20million%20in%20humanitarian%20aid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20massive%20contribution%20will%20total%20more%20than%20most%20countries'%20humanitarian%20aid%20to%20Ukraine%20as%20of%20yet.%20The%20UK%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifw-kiel.de%2Ftopics%2Fwar-against-ukraine%2Fukraine-support-tracker%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econtributed%20%24620%20million%20and%20the%20Netherlands%20has%20provided%20%24780%20million%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20per%20the%20Kiel%20Institute's%20Ukraine%20Support%20tracker.%20The%20foundation's%20contributions%20already%20trounce%20Canada's%20%E2%80%94%20the%20NATO%20country%2C%20which%20has%20a%20significant%20Ukrainian%20diaspora%2C%20has%20given%20%24292%20million%20in%20humanitarian%20aid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnybody%20who%20feels%20that%20Ukraine%20doesn't%20need%20our%20support%20is%20failing%20to%20recognize%20what%20Zelenskyy%20is%20leading%20his%20country%20against%2C%20and%20it's%20it's%20an%20incredible%20force%20that%20he's%20up%20against%2C%26quot%3B%20Buffett%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuffett%20attributes%20the%20US'%20dwindling%20support%20for%20Ukraine%20to%20politics.%20It%20was%20standing%20in%20the%20way%20of%20supporting%20a%20country%20%26quot%3Bthat%20is%20fighting%20for%20its%20freedom%2C%20its%20democracy%2C%20its%20sovereignty%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20Buffett%2C%20the%20only%20choice%20America%20has%20is%20to%20ramp%20up%20support%3A%20%26quot%3BEither%20we%20stand%20with%20NATO%20and%20fight%2C%20which%20is%20what%20I%20think%20the%20only%20option%20is%2C%20or%20if%20we%20say%20we're%20not%20going%20to%20support%20NATO%2C%20we%20are%20going%20to%20be%20in%20a%20world%20of%20hurt%20down%20the%20road.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22American%20billionaire%20Howard%20Buffet%20(L)%20receives%20advice%20from%20his%20Ukrainian%20security%20while%20wearing%20body%20armor%20and%20a%20helmet%20on%20the%20frontlines%20on%20June%2015%2C%202023%2C%20in%20Zolota%20Nyva%2C%20Donetsk%20district%2C%20Ukraine.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ce25f4a610a9069d5935b5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223985%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAmerican%20billionaire%20Howard%20Buffet%20(L)%20receives%20advice%20from%20his%20Ukrainian%20security%20while%20wearing%20body%20armor%20and%20a%20helmet%20on%20the%20frontlines%20on%20June%2015%2C%202023%2C%20in%20Zolota%20Nyva%2C%20Donetsk%20district%2C%20Ukraine.%3Cp%3EPaula%20Bronstein.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBuffett's%20foundation%20has%20helped%20revitalize%20agricultural%20infrastructure%2C%20aid%20civilian%20areas%20affected%20by%20conflict%2C%20replace%20shattered%20windows%2C%20facilitate%20mine%20clearance%20efforts%2C%20and%20provide%20vital%20equipment%20for%20security%20officials%20and%20healthcare%20facilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20foundation%20began%20by%20providing%20food%20kits%20to%20recaptured%20territories%20on%20the%20eastern%20front%20in%202022.%20They%20also%20dedicated%20themselves%20to%20de-mining%20efforts%20and%20boosting%20local%20agriculture%20by%20providing%20equipment%2C%20seeds%2C%20fertilizer%2C%20and%20vegetable%20seeds%20for%20home%20gardens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuffett%20called%20Ukraine's%20current%20food%20insecurity%20crisis%20%26quot%3Bironic%26quot%3B%20given%20its%20reputation%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bbreadbasket%20of%20Europe.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20standing%20there%20giving%20food%20to%20somebody%20who%20all%20their%20life%20has%20produced%20food%20for%20other%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUkraine%20was%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20suppliers%20to%20the%20World%20Food%20Programme%20for%20food%20assistance%20worldwide%2C%20so%20it%20really%20disrupted%20their%20process%20when%20the%20war%20broke%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20observed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E'The%20world%20is%20less%20safe%20now%20than%20it%20was%20before%20Putin%20invaded%20Ukraine'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22On%20a%20humanitarian%20mission%2C%20Howard%20G.%20Buffet%20(left)%20shakes%20hands%20with%20Kherson%20Governor%20Oleksandr%20Prokudin%20as%20they%20hold%20a%20meeting%20concerning%20reconstruction%20efforts%20after%20the%20devastating%20floods%2C%20on%20June%2020%2C%202023%2C%20in%20Kherson%2C%20Ukraine.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c62ce9917a1dae0244d6da%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223601%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOn%20a%20humanitarian%20mission%2C%20Howard%20G.%20Buffet%20(left)%20shakes%20hands%20with%20Kherson%20Governor%20Oleksandr%20Prokudin%20as%20they%20hold%20a%20meeting%20concerning%20reconstruction%20efforts%20after%20the%20devastating%20floods%2C%20on%20June%2020%2C%202023%2C%20in%20Kherson%2C%20Ukraine.%3Cp%3EPaula%20Bronstein.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHoward%20Buffett%20said%20that%20while%20he%20speaks%20to%20his%20father%20about%20the%20situation%20in%20Ukraine%20extensively%2C%20he%20intends%20to%20keep%20those%20conversations%20private.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Howard%20Buffett%20has%20lent%20his%20voice%20to%20political%20advocacy%2C%20speaking%20out%20to%20support%20Ukraine%20and%20advocating%20for%20increased%20international%20support%20and%20military%20aid%20to%20the%20war-torn%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20world%20is%20less%20safe%20now%20than%20it%20was%20before%20Putin%20invaded%20Ukraine%2C%20and%20it%20will%20be%20much%20less%20safe%20if%20Putin%20is%20successful%20with%20Ukraine.%20And%20obvious