February%2025%2C%20instead%20of%20cars%20and%20buses%20running%20down%20Novyi%20Arbat%2C%20it%20was%20police%20vans%2C%20sirens%20blaring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%2C%20anti-war%20protesters%20were%20being%20tackled%20to%20the%20ground%20by%20black-clad%20police%20officers%20and%20the%20National%20Guard.%20They%20cried%20out%20and%20screamed%2C%20often%20with%20tears%20of%20anger%20in%20their%20eyes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20who%20didn't%20have%20the%20confidence%20to%20wave%20placards%20placed%20anti-war%20stickers%20on%20their%20rucksacks%2C%20sprayed%20graffiti%20on%20walls%20or%20left%20green%20ribbons%20on%20park%20benches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20those%20early%20weeks%20of%20the%20invasion%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-arrests-anti-war-protesters-ukraine-invasion-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20than%2015%2C000%20protesters%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20thrown%20behind%20bars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225472%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Security%20forces%20mass%20during%20an%20anti-war%20protest%20in%20Moscow%2C%20Russia%20on%20March%2006%2C%202022.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d8a81dce7f1785b2e36333%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223648%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESecurity%20forces%20mass%20during%20an%20anti-war%20protest%20in%20Moscow%2C%20Russia%20on%20March%2006%2C%202022.%3Cp%3EStringer%2FAnadolu%20Agency%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20plugged%20into%20what%20was%20happening%20made%20the%20savvy%20move%20to%20withdraw%20savings%20from%20local%20banks%20and%20exchange%20them%20for%20dollars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20just%20a%20few%20days%2C%20the%20Russian%20ruble%20would%20collapse%20from%2076%20rubles%20to%20the%20dollar%20to%20134.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20foreign%20friends%20initially%20made%20dark%20jokes%20about%20how%20much%20their%20salaries%2C%20paid%20in%20international%20currencies%2C%20were%20now%20wo