0finished%20the%20day%20trailing%20England%20by%20134%20runs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Modi%E2%80%99s%20Call%20for%20370%20Seats%20Is%20Echoed%20by%20Bollywood%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F24142346%2Fimage-1870.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EThis%20piece%20was%20first%20published%20on%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theindiacable.com%2Fp%2Firked-by-fascism-charge-modis-censors%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3EThe%20India%20Cable%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%93%C2%A0a%20premium%20newsletter%20from%C2%A0The%20Wire%20%26amp%3B%20Galileo%20Ideas%20%E2%80%93%20and%20has%20been%20republished%20here.%20To%20subscribe%20to%20The%20India%20Cable%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theindiacable.com%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3Eclick%20here%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20been%20exhorting%20his%20party%20workers%20to%20work%20for%20370%20seats.%20He%20predicts%20the%20BJP%20itself%20will%20get%20that%20number%2C%20and%20along%20with%20the%20allies%2C%20get%20around%20400.%20In%202019%2C%20the%20BJP%20won%20303%20seats%2C%20so%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20pretty%20big%20jump%20of%20about%2067%20seats%2C%20not%20an%20easy%20electoral%20feat%20that%20Modi%20is%20predicting.%20Why%20370%3F%20If%20the%20idea%20is%20to%20touch%20a%20two-third%20majority%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20358%20seats%20should%20be%20enough.%20Nor%20is%20370%20higher%20than%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20400%20plus%20in%20the%201984%20elections.%20So%20how%20did%20Modi%20choose%20the%20number%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20obvious%20really%20%E2%80%93%20370%20is%20also%20the%20number%20of%20the%20Article%20in%20the%20Constitution%20that%20gave%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20its%20special%20status%20within%20the%20Union%20of%20India.%20Getting%20rid%20of%20this%20Article%20was%20the%20first%20major%20decision%20of%20the%20BJP%20government%20after%202019.%20Lest%20voters%20forget%2C%20this%20call%20by%20the%20prime%20minister%20will%20remind%20them%20of%20that.%20And%20the%20media%20%E2%80%93%20especially%20the%20television%20channels%20will%20do%20their%20part%2C%20constantly%20talking%20about%20Mission%20370%20on%20the%20nightly%20news.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20clever%20by-half%20tactic%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20kind%20that%20it%20specialises%20in.%20The%20idea%20is%20to%20always%20remind%20the%20people%20of%20its%20agenda%20and%20its%20%E2%80%98achievements%E2%80%99%2C%20so%20that%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20forget.%20And%20they%20corral%20social%20media%20supporters%2C%20mainstream%20Godi%20media%20and%20of%20course%20fellow%20traveller%20popular%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERight%20on%20cue%2C%20arrives%20%3Cem%3EArticle%20370%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20film%20starring%20Yami%20Gautam%20and%20Arun%20Govil%20(who%20once%20played%20Ram%20in%20the%20TV%20serial%20%3Cem%3ERamayan%3C%2Fem%3E).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20synopsis%20of%20the%20film%20on%20the%20site%20%E2%80%98Book%20my%20Show%2C%E2%80%99%20where%20one%20can%20buy%20tickets%20for%20movies%2C%20reads%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%202016%20Kashmir%20unrest%2C%20a%20young%20local%20field%20agent%2C%20Zooni%20Haksar%2C%20is%20picked%20out%20by%20Rajeshwari%20Swaminathan%20from%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Office%20for%20a%20top-secret%20mission.%20Their%20aim%3F%20Cracking%20down%20on%20terrorism%20and%20putting%20an%20end%20to%20the%20billion-dollar%20conflict%20economy%20in%20the%20valley%2C%20by%20doing%20the%20absolute%20impossible%20%E2%80%93%20abrogating%20the%20notorious%20Article%20370.%20That%20too%2C%20without%20spilling%20a%20single%20drop%20of%20innocent%20blood.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELots%20of%20guns%2C%20explosions%2C%20and%20killings