and%20Kangana%20Ranaut%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EEmergency%3C%2Fem%3E.%20No%20doubt%20a%20few%20more%20will%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20all%20such%20overly%20nationalistic%20and%20propaganda%20films%20have%20been%20successful.%20A%20recent%20biopic%20of%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20sank%20without%20a%20trace%2C%20as%20did%20Akshay%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20big-budget%20%3Cem%3ESamrat%20Prithviraj%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20touted%20as%20a%20Hindutva%20film.%20But%20small%20films%20without%20stars%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Kashmir%20Files%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Kerala%20Story%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20did%20well%20and%20such%20movies%20do%20get%20traction%20on%20social%20media%20even%20if%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20succeed%20at%20the%20box%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20BJP%2C%20however%2C%20flops%20or%20hits%2C%20each%20of%20these%20films%20adds%20to%20the%20noise%20it%20creates%20and%20are%20force%20multipliers.%20They%20confirm%20the%20prejudices%20of%20its%20followers%20and%20potential%20voters%2C%20especially%20from%20a%20younger%20demographic%20who%20will%20probably%20%E2%80%98learn%E2%80%99%20their%20history%20from%20this.%20And%20as%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20open%20support%20for%20%3Cem%3EArticle%20370%3C%2Fem%3E%20shows%2C%20the%20BJP%2C%20on%20its%20part%2C%20will%20throw%20its%20full%20weight%20behind%20those%20projects%2C%20such%20as%20Article%20370%2C%20it%20thinks%20will%20help%20its%20mission%20of%20getting%20those%20370%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708774247000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F24142346%2Fimage-1870.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fmodis-call-for-370-seats-is-echoed-by-bollywood%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22How%20did%20Modi%20choose%20the%20number%3F%20It's%20obvious%20really%20%E2%80%93%20370%20is%20also%20the%20number%20of%20the%20Article%20in%20the%20Constitution%20that%20gave%20J%26amp%3BK%20its%20special%20status%20within%20the%20Union%20of%20I