%20to%20personal%20reasons%2C%20before%20also%20making%20himself%20unavailable%20for%20the%20remainder%20of%20the%20series.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UP%20Cancels%20Police%20Constable%20Recruitment%20Exam%20After%20Paper%20Leak%20Allegations%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%20on%20Saturday%20cancelled%20the%20recently%20held%20police%20constable%20recruitment%20examination%20following%20allegations%20of%20question%20paper%20leak%20and%20ordered%20a%20re-test%20within%20six%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20government%20also%20announced%20a%20probe%20into%20the%20allegations%20by%20the%20Special%20Task%20Force%20(STF).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%2048%20lakh%20candidates%20appeared%20in%20the%20examination%20conducted%20on%20February%2017%20and%2018%20across%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20in%20Hindi%20on%20'X'%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20can%20be%20no%20compromise%20with%20the%20sanctity%20of%20examinations.%20Those%20who%20toy%20with%20the%20hard%20work%20of%20youngsters%20will%20not%20be%20spared%20under%20any%20circumstances.%20Strictest%20action%20is%20certain%20to%20be%20taken%20against%20such%20unruly%20elements.%26quot%3B%20More%20than%20240%20people%20were%20arrested%20and%20detained%20by%20police%20across%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20for%20allegedly%20adopting%20or%20planning%20to%20use%20unfair%20means%20in%20the%20recruitment%20exam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccouncing%20the%20decision%2C%20the%20state%20home%20department%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOn%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20information%20and%20facts%20pertaining%20to%20police%20recruitment%20examination%20held%20on%20February%2017%20and%20February%2018%2C%20the%20government%2C%20while%20keeping%20in%20mind%20the%20highest%20standards%20of%20sanctity%20and%20transparency%2C%20has%20decided%20to%20cancel%20the%20examination.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThe%20government%20has%20directed%20the%20recruitment%20board%20to%20register%20an%20FIR%20at%20the%20level%20where%20laxity%20has%20been%20committed%20and%20ensure%20further%20action.%20The%20government%20has%20decided%20to%20get%20the%20matter%20probed%20by%20the%20STF.%20Directions%20have%20also%20been%20issued%20to%20take%20strictest%20action%20against%20the%20guilty%20persons%20and%20organisation%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20statement%2C%20a%20re-examination%20will%20be%20conducted%20within%20six%20months%20and%20UPSRTC%20buses%20will%20ferry%20candidates%20to%20the%20centres%20for%20free.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20the%20development%2C%20senior%20AAP%20leader%20in%20the%20state%20Shekhar%20Dixit%20told%20PTI%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20cannot%20be%20anything%20more%20saddening%20than%20leakage%20of%20examination%20question%20paper.%20Earlier%2C%20question%20paper%20leaks%20were%20unheard%20of%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh...%20The%20leakage%20of%20the%20question%20paper%20proves%20that%20the%20education%20mafia%20is%20still%20very%20strong%20in%20the%20state.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708772940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fuoe0vapg_exam-generic-pixabay_625x300_17_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-cancels-police-constable-recruitment-exam-after-paper-leak-allegations-5118905%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%20on%20Saturday%20cancelled%20the%20recently%20held%20police%20constable%20recruitment%20examination%20following%20allegations%20of%20question%20paper%20leak%20and%20ordered%20a%20re-test%20within%20six%20months.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-cancels-police-constable-recruitment-exam-after-paper-leak-allegations-5118905%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-cancels-police-constable-recruitment-exam-after-paper-leak-allegations-5118905%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-cancels-police-constable-recruitment-exam-after-paper-leak-allegations-5118905%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%20%7C%20'Modi%E2%80%99s%20Supremacy%20a%20Threat%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20Success%2C%20Stifling%20its%20Rise'%3A%20Ramachandra%20Guha%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F24163201%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-24-at-15.06.26.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20well-known%20and%20highly%20regarded%20historian%20of%20modern%20India%20and%20one%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20foremost%20political%20commentators%2C%20Ramachandra%20Guha%2C%20has%20said%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20supremacy%2C%20by%20which%20he%20means%20his%20personality%2C%20his%20style%20of%20governance%2C%20and%20the%20policies%20he%20has%20pursued%20for%20the%20last%2010%20years%2C%20is%20a%20threat%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGuha%20said%20that%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cbulldozer%20approach%E2%80%9D%20and%20his%20%E2%80%9Cone-size-fits-all%E2%80%9D%20strategy%20are%20hindering%20India%E2%80%99s%20potential.%20He%20further%20said%20that%20Modi%20poses%20not%20only%20a%20threat%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20progress%20but%20is%20also%2C%20in%20that%20regard%2C%20%E2%80%9Cdangerous.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%2035-minute%20interview%20to%20Karan%20Thapar%20for%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Guha%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CModi%20sees%20himself%20as%20a%20new%20emperor%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommenting%20that%20psychiatrists%20might%20need%20to%20study%20it%2C%20Guha%20spoke%20about%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20delusions%20of%20grandeur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20discussing%20his%20recent%20essay%20on%20foreign%20affairs%2C%20titled%20%E2%80%98How%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20supremacy%20will%20hinder%20his%20country%E2%80%99s%20rise%E2%80%99%2C%20Guha%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20very%20nature%20of%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20authority%2C%20the%20aggressive%20control%20sought%20by%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20his%20party%20over%20a%20staggeringly%20diverse%20and%20complicated%20country%2C%20threatens%20to%20scupper%20India%E2%80%99s%20great-power%20ambitions%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20said%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20personality%20and%20style%20of%20government%20%E2%80%9Cis%20jeopardising%20a%20key%20source%20of%20Indian%20strength%3A%20its%20varied%20forms%20of%20pluralism%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20party%2C%20the%20BJP%2C%20and%20within%20it%2C%20one%20man%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20are%20judged%20to%20represent%20India%20to%20itself%20and%20to%20the%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20The%20result%20is%20%E2%80%9CHindus%20impose%20themselves%20on%20Muslims%2C%20the%20central%20government%20imposes%20itself%20on%20the%20provinces%2C%20the%20state%20further%20curtails%20the%20rights%20and%20freedoms%20of%20citizens.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20unthinking%20imitation%20of%20Western%20models%20of%20energy-intensive%20and%20capital-intensive%20industrialization%20is%20causing%20profound%20and%2C%20in%20many%20cases%2C%20irreversible%20environmental%20damage.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%20there%20is%20a%20huge%20paradox%20which%20Guha%20readily%20accepts.%20Modi%20is%20hugely%20popular%2C%20the%20country%20loves%20him%2C%20and%20he%20is%20very%20likely%20to%20be%20re-elected%20for%20a%20third%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CModi%20remains%20extremely%20popular.%20He%20is%20incredibly%20hardworking%20and%20politically%20astute.%20%5BHe%E2%80%99s%5D%20able%20to%20read%20the%20pulse%20of%20the%20electorate%20and%20adapts%20his%20rhetoric%20and%20tactics%20accordingly.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGuha%20agrees%20this%20means%20we%20have%20a%20master%20politician%20and%20tactician%20ruling%20us%20.%20A%20man%20who%20is%20incredibly%20popular%20and%20powerful.%20But%20he%E2%80%99s%20also%20authoritarian%20and%20majoritarian%20in%20his%20approach.%20And%20he%E2%80%99s%20implementing%20policies%20that%20are%2C%20in%20many%20instances%2C%20disturbing%2C%20divisive%20and%20even%2C%20potentially%2C%20destructive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Febj31A3bT8U%3Fsi%3DdXNRRtV5wNzNLrzK%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708772562000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F24163201%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-24-at-15.06.26.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-modis-supremacy-a-threat-to-indias-success-stifling-its-rise-ramachandra-guha%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Guha%20told%20Karan%20Thapar%20that%20Modi's%20'bulldozer%20approach'%20and%20his%20'one-size-fits-all'%20strategy%20are%20hindering%20India's%20potential.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-modis-supremacy-a-threat-to-indias-success-stifling-its-rise-ramachandra-guha%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Team%20of%20cheaters'%3A%20Fans%20accuse%20England%20of%20lacking%20sportsman%20spirit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708772386000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107967646%2Cimgsize-49242.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22http