n-ashwin-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERavichandran%20Ashwin%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20bowlers%20put%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20effort.%20Ashwin%2C%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%2C%20and%20both%20the%20fast%20bowlers%20put%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20effort.%20Siraj%20bowled%20better%20in%20his%20second%20spell%20than%20his%20first.%20The%20only%20thing%20I%20have%20a%20doubt%20about%20is%20that%20you%20didn't%20use%20Kuldeep%20Yadav%20as%20much%20as%20you%20should%20have%2C%26quot%3B%20RP%20Singh%20said%20on%20Jio%20Cinema.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJadeja%20and%20Ashwin%20were%20over%20bowled%20and%20Kuldeep%20couldn't%20bowl%20that%20much%20because%20of%20that%2C%20and%20this%20happens%20as%20well.%20When%20you%20have%20three%20spinners%2C%20and%20all%20three%20are%20wicket-takers%2C%20one%20of%20the%20bowlers%20is%20underbowled%20many%20times%20and%20that%20happened%20with%20Kuldeep%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChopra%20explained%20that%20Rohit%20had%20too%20many%20options%20in%20the%20bowling%20department%2C%20comparing%20his%20situation%20like%20going%20to%20a%20buffet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20right%2C%20you%20are%20spoilt%20for%20choices%20when%20you%20have%20five%20bowlers.%20You%20get%20confused%20at%20times%20when%20you%20go%20to%20a%20buffet.%20Kuldeep%20Yadav%20was%20100%25%20introduced%20late.%20He%20could%20have%20been%20bowled%20a%20little%20earlier%2C%26quot%3B%20Chopra%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20debutant%20pacer%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Akash%20Deep%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F113443-akash-deep-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAkash%20Deep%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20the%20pick%20of%20the%20bowlers%20for%20India%20on%20Day%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20struck%20thrice%20in%20the%20first%20session%20to%20end%20the%20day%20with%20figures%20of%203%2F70.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bengal%20pacer%20got%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ben%20Duckett%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports