indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fus-senator-calls-on-pakistani-authorities-to-probe-allegations-of-fraud-in-february-8-polls%2Famp_articleshow%2F107966024.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Changes%20After%20Assam%20Scraps%20Muslim%20Marriage%20Registration%20Law%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Assam%20government%20has%20decided%20to%20repeal%20the%20personal%20law%20governing%20marriages%20and%20divorces%20among%20Muslims%20in%20a%20big%20push%20towards%20a%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20(ICC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUCC%20refers%20to%20a%20common%20set%20of%20laws%20applicable%20to%20all%20Indian%20citizens%20and%20is%20not%20based%20on%20religion%20in%20dealing%20with%20personal%20matters%20like%20marriage%2C%20divorce%2C%20inheritance%2C%20and%20adoption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Uttarakhand%20becoming%20the%20first%20state%20to%20pass%20a%20UCC%20law%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20Assam%20has%20been%20hinting%20at%20bringing%20a%20similar%20law.%20There's%20a%20buzz%20that%20the%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20government%20may%20introduce%20a%20UCC%20bill%20during%20the%20Budget%20session%20that%20ends%20February%2028.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20first%20step%20towards%20this%2C%20Assam%20Minister%20Jayanta%20Malla%20Baruah%20said%20on%20Friday%20the%20cabinet%20has%20decided%20to%20repeal%20the%20Muslim%20Marriage%20and%20Divorce%20Registration%20Act.%20The%20government%20now%20wants%20to%20bring%20all%20such%20matters%20under%20the%20Special%20Marriage%20Act%2C%20said%20Mr%20Baruah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20will%20change%20after%20the%20law%20is%20repealed%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EFormalise%20Registration%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20law%20allows%20voluntary%20registration%20of%20marriages%20and%20divorces%20among%20Muslims.%20It%20is%20not%20mandatory%20under%20the%20law%20to%20register%20such%20instances.%20The%20registration%20machinery%20too%20is%20informal%20which%20provides%20for%20a%20scope%20for%20non-compliance%20with%20extant%20norms%2C%20said%20Mr%20Sarma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20More%20Muslim%20Registrars%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuslim%20registrars%20holding%20licenses%20to%20register%20marriages%20and%20divorces%20in%20the%20community%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20register%20marriages%20and%20divorces%20once%20the%20law%20is%20repealed.%20Mr%20Baruah%20has%20said%2094%20Muslim%20registrars%2C%20who%20have%20been%20registering%20marriages%20under%20the%20law%2C%20will%20be%20given%20a%20one-time%20compensation%20of%20Rs%202%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECustody%20of%20Registration%20Records%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20law%20is%20scrapped%2C%20the%20district%20commissioners%20and%20district%20registrars%20will%20have%20the%20%26quot%3Bcustody%20of%20registration%20records%26quot%3B%2C%20according%20to%20Mr%20Sarma.%20The%20registrations%20will%20be%20done%20under%20the%20supervision%20and%20control%20of%20the%20Assam%20Inspector%20General%20of%20Registration.%20Currently%2C%20the%2094%20Muslim%20Marriage%20Registrars%20hold%20the%20authority%20to%20be%20the%20custodians%20of%20such%20records.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrevent%20Child%20Marriages%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECertain%20provisions%20in%20the%20current%20law%20allow%20marriages%20to%20be%20registered%20even%20if%20the%20bride%20and%20the%20groom%20have%20not%20reached%20the%20legal%20age%20of%2018%20and%2021%2C%20said%20Mr%20Sarma%2C%20adding%20that%20its%20scrapping%20will%20mark%20a%20significant%20step%20towards%20stopping%20child%20marriages%20in%20Assam.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708768320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-08%2F1346v45g_himanta-biswa-sarma-pti_625x300_11_August_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-changes-after-assam-scraps-muslim-marriage-registration-law-5118231%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Assam%20government%20has%20decided%20to%20r