0branches%2C%20and%20twigs.%20Women%20wielded%20sticks%20and%20brooms%20in%20various%20places.%20Villagers%20obstructed%20roads%20by%20uprooting%20trees%20and%20lampposts.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20villagers%20claimed%20that%20men%20and%20students%20were%20taken%20into%20custody%20after%20an%20attack%20on%20Maity%E2%80%99s%20house.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDirector%20General%20of%20Police%20(South%20Bengal)%20Supratim%20Sarkar%20and%20the%20state%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%20Rajeev%20Kumar%20rushed%20to%20the%20location%20to%20address%20the%20situation.%20Subsequently%2C%20prohibitory%20orders%20under%20Section%20144%20of%20the%20Code%20of%20Criminal%20Procedure%20were%20imposed%20in%20Bermajur%20Gram%20Panchayat%20I%20and%20II%2C%20along%20with%20other%20regions%20like%20Situlia%20Bazar%2C%20Hatgachhia%2C%20Trimoni%20Bazar%2C%20Khulna%20Ghat%2C%20and%20Haldarpara%20in%20Jelliakhali.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20incident%20comes%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20fresh%20tensions%20in%20Jhupkhali%2C%20another%20village%20in%20Sandeshkhali%20Block%202%20about%2010%20kilometres%20from%20the%20centre%20of%20the%20protest.%20On%20February%2022%2C%20villagers%20are%20learned%20to%20have%20set%20fire%20to%20the%20office%20of%20a%20fishery%20allegedly%20controlled%20by%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan%E2%80%99s%20brother%2C%20Sirajuddin.%20The%20escalation%20and%20extension%20of%20unrest%20across%20two%20blocks%20in%20Sandeshkhali%20have%20added%20to%20the%20mounting%20political%20difficulties%20for%20West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20with%20the%20elections%20impending.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fsandeshkhali-journalists-tmc-bjp-rape-allegations-bengal%5C%22%3ESandeshkhali%3A%20Crackdown%20on%20Journalists%20and%20Politicians%E2%80%99%20Name-Calling%20Amid%20Rape%20Allegations%20Rock%20Bengal%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20Left%20Front%20government%2C%20these%20lands%20were%20distributed%20to%20local%20farmers%2C%20who%20have%20been%20cultivating%20them.%20Last%20year%2C%20Ajit%20Maity%2C%20leading%20Shahjahan%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9CCobra%20Army%E2%80%9D%20came%20and%20beat%20us%20all%20up.%20They%20forcibly%20evicted%20farmers%20from%20around%2042%20bighas%20(26%20acres)%20of%20land%20without%20any%20compensation%2C%E2%80%9D%20s%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eaid%20Pintu%20Sardar%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20the%20area%2C%20who%20was%20present%20during%20the%20protests.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPintu%20said%20that%20even%20traditional%20TMC%20supporters%20are%20not%20spared%20the%20local%20leaders%E2%80%99%20wrath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CShibu%20%5BHazra%2C%20one%20of%20those%20accused%20alongside%20Shahjahan%5D%20and%20Uttam%20%5Banother%20accused%5D%2C%20they%20are%20outsiders.%20They%20live%20in%20another%20village.%20They%20are%20being%20supported%20by%20some%20ministers%20and%20leaders%20in%20their%20effort%20to%20loot%20and%20torture%20villagers.%20Even%20the%20women%20have%20raised%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20stated%20Tapas%20Das%2C%20who%20has%20been%20associated%20with%20Trinamool%20Congress%20since%20its%20inception.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBermajur%20and%20the%20state%20of%20things%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBermajur%2C%20a%20place%20with%20historical%20significance%2C%20was%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20Tebhaga%20movement%20in%201946%2C%20where%20a%20clash%20between%20landlords%20and%20sharecroppers%20resulted%20in%20the%20death%20of%20five%20farmers.%20Locals%20claim%20that%20Shahjahan%E2%80%99s%20forces%20demolished%20a%20memorial%20linked%20to%20the%20movement.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20On%20Thursday%2C%20another%20playing%20field%20which%20had%20long%20since%20been%20under%20lock%20and%20key%20%E2%80%93%20named%20%E2%80%98Rishi%20Arabinda%20Maidan%E2%80%99%20and%20forcefully%20held%20by%20the%20%E2%80%98Sheikh%20Shahjahan%20Fan%20Club%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20was%20reclaimed%20by%20villagers%20and%20thrown%20to%20the%20public.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F24143130%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-22-at-2.21.10-PM-1024x664.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F24143130%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-22-at-2.21.10-PM-1024x664.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F24143130%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-22-at-2.21.10-PM-300x194.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F24143130%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-22-at-2.21.10-PM.jpeg%201080w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-698667%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22545%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20man%20paints%20over%20the%20sign%20%E2%80%98Sheikh%20Shahjahan%20Fan%20Club%E2%80%99.%20Photo%3A%20By%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Dhamakhali%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20spoke%20to%20Jamshed%20Molla%2C%20a%20senior%20citizen.%20He%20displayed%20all%20the%20legal%20documents%20for%20his%20land.%20Jamshed%20said%20he%20was%20in%20the%20process%20of%20constructing%20a%20house%2C%20when%20Alim%20Molla%2C%20associated%20with%20Shahjahan%E2%80%99s%20gang%2C%20intervened.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAlim%20declared%20that%20the%20land%20did%20not%20belong%20to%20me%20and%20stopped%20me%20from%20building%20the%20house.%20Shah%20Jahan%E2%80%99s%20army%20also%20took%20my%20brother%E2%80%99s%20land.%20When%20I%20went%20to%20report%20to%20the%20Sandeshkhali%20police%20station%2C%20police%20asked%20me%20to%20settle%20the%20matter%20amongst%20ourselves%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Jamshed%20Mollah.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Majherpara%2C%20women%20point%20to%20a%20massive%20fishery%20of%20500%20acres%20called%20%E2%80%98Akhashbheri%E2%80%99.%20Locals%20claim%20that%20in%202021%2C%20the%20multi-crop%20land%20was%20forcefully%20grabbed%20by%20Shibu%20Hazra%20%E2%80%93%20who%20was%20recently%20arrested%20%E2%80%93%20who%20pumped%20salt%20water%20just%20before%20harvesting.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20BDO%20office%20is%20a%20mere%20five-minute%20walk%20from%20here.%20The%20police%20station%20is%20located%20just%20behind%20it.%20Many%20of%20us%20toiled%20to%20cultivate%20this%20land.%20Were%20we%20all%20silent%20when%20it%20was%20taken%20away%3F%20No.%20There%20were%20screams%20and%20cries.%20Some%20even%20approached%20the%20police%2C%20reporting%20that%20everything%20was%20being%20seized%20from%20them%E2%80%9D%20asked%20a%20woman%20who%20requested%20anonymity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fsandeshkhali-unrest-as-women-led-protests-escalate-tmcs-outsider-claims-find-little-resonance%5C%22%3ESandeshkhali%20Unrest%3A%20As%20Women-Led%20Protests%20Escalate%2C%20TMC%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Outsider%E2%80%99%20Claims%20Find%20Little%20Resonance%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPolitics%20over%20sexual%20harassment%20claims%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETMC%20has%20been%20raising%20questions%20about%20the%20prolonged%20silence%20of%20the%20alleged%20abuse%20victims%2C%20emphasising%20on%20the%20lack%20of%20complaints%20from%20either%20the%20victims%20or%20the%20opposition%20party.%20While%20the%20police%20have%20%E2%80%93%20after%20a%20delay%20%E2%80%93%20filed%20at%20least%20two%20cases%20of%20gang%20rape%20against%20Sibu%20Hazra%20and%20Uttam%20Sardar%2C%20TMC%20spokespersons%20have%20demanded%20video%20evidence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20spoke%20to%20several%20Sandeshkhali%20women%20who%20alleged%20layers%20of%20abuse%20by%20local%20TMC%20leaders%2C%20include%20grave%20accounts%20of%20sexual%20harassment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EProtesters%20have%20found%20solidarity%20from%20a%20faction%20within%20the%20TMC%20which%20has%20been%20saying%20that%20they%20too%20have%20been%20victims%20of%20the%20abuse%20of%20power%20by%20Shahjahan%2C%20Shibu%20Hazra%2C%20and%20Uttam%20Sardar.%20Long-time%20TMC%20leader%20Sudeb%20Giri%20shared%20his%20experience.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20beat%20me%20so%20much%20that%20I%20could%20not%20get%20out%20of%20bed%20for%20two%20months.%20We%20complained%20to%20Didi.%20Balu%20Da%20(arrested%20minister%20Jyotipriya%20Mallick)%20was%20aware%20of%20everything%2C%20yet%20supported%20Shahjahan.%20And%20the%20police%20are%20with%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20Giri%20claimed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20banks%20of%20Kalagachia%20river%2C%20a%20group%20of%20women%2C%20their%20faces%20veiled%2C%20approached%20this%20reporter.%20They%20also%20claimed%20that%20Mallick%20was%20responsible%20for%20Shahjahan%E2%80%99s%20complete%20control%20over%20the%20region%2C%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20very%20safety%20of%20locals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20speak%20up%2C%20they%20hurt%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20one%20woman%20said.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20stay%20silent%2C%20we%20suffer.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20the%20Bengali%20original%20by%20Aparna%20Bhattacharya.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708766770000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fsandeshkhali-tmc-trinamool-protest-women%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Wire%20spoke%20to%20several%20Sandeshkhali%