t%2C%201935%2C%20in%20what%20an%20Assam%20minister%20termed%20as%20a%20significant%20step%20forward%20towards%20implementing%20the%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20(UCC)%20in%20the%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20chief%20minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20claimed%20that%20the%20decision%20will%20help%20the%20government%20prevent%20child%20marriages%20in%20the%20state%2C%20his%20cabinet%20minister%20Jayanta%20Malla%20Baruah%20laid%20out%20a%20larger%20motivation%20behind%20the%20move%2C%20that%20is%20to%20implement%20the%20UCC%20in%20Assam.%20Baruah%20also%20said%20that%20the%20existing%20law%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccolonial%20Act%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETaking%20to%20X%20(formerly%20called%20Twitter)%2C%20Sarma%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9COn%20February%2023%2C%20the%20Assam%20cabinet%20made%20a%20significant%20decision%20to%20repeal%20the%20age-old%20Assam%20Muslim%20Marriages%20and%20Divorces%20Registration%20Act.%20This%20act%20contained%20provisions%20allowing%20marriage%20registration%20even%20if%20the%20bride%20and%20groom%20had%20not%20reached%20the%20legal%20ages%20of%2018%20and%2021%2C%20as%20required%20by%20the%20law.%20This%20move%20marks%20another%20significant%20step%20towards%20prohibiting%20child%20marriages%20in%20Assam.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fhimanta-chartered-flights-helicopter-assam-assembly%5C%22%3ERs%2058%2C23%2C07%2C104%3A%20Public%20Money%20Spent%20on%20CM%20Himanta%2C%20Other%20VIPs%E2%80%99%20Air%20Travel%2C%20According%20to%20Assam%20Govt%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESarma%20has%20been%20leading%20a%20campaign%20against%20child%20marriages%2C%20but%20his%20critics%20claim%20that%20the%20campaign%20has%20mostly%20targeted%20Muslim%20families%20of%20the%20state%20and%20has%20visible%20communal%20undertones.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20on%20Friday%2C%20Sarma%20said%20that%20the%20need%20to%20repeal%20the%20Act%20arose%20because%20it%20does%20not%20require%20mandatory%20registration%20of%20marriages%20and%20divorces%2C%20and%20is%20only%20voluntary%2C%20leaving%20much%20scope%20for%20%E2%80%9Cnon-compliance%20of%20norms%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20per%20provisions%20of%20the%20act%2C%20there%20remains%20scope%20for%20registering%20marriages%20of%20intended%20persons%20below%2021%20years%20(for%20males)%20and%2018%20years%20(for%20females)%20and%20there%20is%20hardly%20any%20monitoring%20for%20implementation%20of%20the%20Act%2C%E2%80%9D%20state%20government%20told%20the%20news%20agency%20ANI.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-will-change-after-repeal-of-assam-muslim-marriage-divorce-registration-law-101708743416744.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20repeal%20of%20the%20Act%20will%20allow%20the%20Assam%20government%E2%80%99s%20district%20commissioners%20and%20district%20registrars%20to%20%E2%80%9Ctake%20custody%20of%20registration%20records%20held%20by%2094%20Muslim%20Marriage%20Registrars%E2%80%9D.%20The%20Muslim%20Marriage%20Registrars%20have%20been%20promised%20a%20one-time%20compensation%20of%20Rs%202%20lakh%20for%20their%20rehabilitation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBaruah%20said%20that%20Muslim%20marriages%20will%20be%20registered%20under%20the%20Special%20Marriage%20Act%2C%20once%20the%20previous%20law%20is%20repealed%2C%20claiming%20that%20the%20Act%20was%20being%20misused%20to%20get%20child%20marriages%20registered.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%C2%A0Assam%3A%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fassam-hindu-group-threatens-christian-schools-to-remove-religious-symbols-or-face-dire-outcome%5C%22%3E%20Hindu%20Group%20Threatens%20Christian%20Schools%20to%20Remove%20Religious%20Symbols%20or%20%E2%80%98Face%20Dire%20Outcome%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20Uttarakhand%2C%20which%20recently%20passed%20the%20UCC%20Bill%2C%20in%20the%20assembly%2C%20the%20Assam%20government%20has%20made%20the%20UCC%20as%20a%20big%20political%20promise%2C%20with%20chief%20minister%20Sarma%20making%20it%20a%20poll%20issue.%20Sarma%20has%20also%20been%20campaigning%20to%20ban%20polygamy%20in%20the%20state%2C%20in%20what%20is%20a%20clear%20aim%20at%20the%20Muslim%20Personal%20Law%2C%20especially%20because%20he%20has%20also%20declared%20that%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20UCC%20Bill%20will%20exempt%20the%20adivasis%20of%20the%20state.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Uttarakhand%20UCC%20Bill%20has%20also%20kept%20the%20tribal%20population%20out%20of%20its%20ambit.%20The%20BJP%20government%20in%20Gujarat%20has%20also%20brought%20a%20UCC%20Bill%20and%20plans%20to%20pass%20it%20in%20the%20state%20assembly%20soon.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20selective%20nature%20of%20the%20UCC%20draft%20Bills%20in%20these%20states%20have%20led%20to%20leaders%20like%20AIMIM%20chief%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%20claiming%20that%20the%20UCC%20violates%20the%20fundamental%20rights%20of%20Indian%20muslims.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708762018000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F08144104%2FGFlamxXa0AAQFxW.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fassam-repeals-muslim-marriages-and-divorces-act-bjp-cites-intent-to-implement-ucc-in-state%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Assam%20CM%20Sarma%20claimed%20that%20the%20decision%20will%20help%20the%20government%20prevent%20child%20marriages%20in%20the%20state.%20However%2C%20his%20critics%20have%20claimed%20that%20the%20campaign%20has%20mostly%20targeted%20Muslim%20families%20of%20the%20state%20and%20has%20visible%20communal%20undertones.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fassam-repeals-muslim-marriages-and-divorces-act-bjp-cites-intent-to-implement-ucc-in-state%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Over%2050%20bn%20tonnes%20transported%20since%20EnduTrax%20inception%3A%20Apollo%20Tyres%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708761929000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107963644%2Cimgsize-128498.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fauto%2Fnews%2Fapollo-tyres-endutrax-tyres-transport-over-50-billion-tonnes-a-technological-milestone%2Farticleshow%2F107963576.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Apollo%20Tyres%20showcased%20their%20EnduTrax%20range%20at%20an%20experiential%20drive%20event.%20With%20a%20strong%20market%20share%20in%20the%20tipper%20segment%2C%20the%20range%20offers%20durability%2C%20resistance%20to%20cuts%20and%20chips%2C%20and%20high-speed%20performance.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22YASH%20SHARMA%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fauto%2Fnews%2Fapollo-tyres-endutrax-tyres-transport-over-50-billion-tonnes-a-technological-milestone%2Farticleshow%2F107963576.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Delhi%20Chalo'%20Protest%20Paused%20Until%20Feb%2029%20as%20Focus%20Turns%20to%20Seeking%20Justice%20for%20Shubhkaran's%20Death%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15145529%2F9313A034-D5C5-4DE6-A64D-6FDBEE5AE65D-1.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChandigarh%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20%E2%80%98Delhi%20Chalo%E2%80%99%20protest%2C%20currently%20halted%20at%20the%20Punjab-Haryana%20borders%20at%20Shambhu%20and%20Khanauri%2C%20has%20been%20further%20suspended%20until%20February%2029.%20Farmer%20leaders%20have%20t