20saying%20they%20demand%20a%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%20to%20be%20registered%20against%20those%20guilty%20of%20Shubhkaran%E2%80%99s%20death.%20While%20speaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Shubh%E2%80%99s%20family%20also%20supported%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmers%20also%20did%20not%20allow%20his%20post-mortem%20and%20cremation%20until%20an%20FIR%20is%20registered%2C%20putting%20the%20government%20in%20a%20major%20fix.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuestioning%20the%20delay%2C%20farmer%20leader%20Pandher%20told%20the%20media%20that%20soon%20after%20Shubhkaran%E2%80%99s%20death%2C%20Punjab%20chief%20minister%20Mann%20had%20said%20that%20action%20would%20be%20taken%20against%20the%20culprits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20his%20own%20officials%20told%20us%20today%20that%20this%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20done.%20This%20is%20unacceptable%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pandher%20told%20the%20press%20at%20Rajindra%20Hospital%20in%20Patiala%2C%20where%20Shubhkaran%E2%80%99s%20dead%20body%20is%20kept%20in%20a%20mortuary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20if%20proper%20action%20is%20not%20taken%20against%20those%20responsible%20for%20Shubhkaran%E2%80%99s%20death%2C%20there%20will%20be%20more%20such%20deaths%20in%20the%20course%20of%20the%20ongoing%20protest%2C%20which%20cannot%20be%20tolerated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolitical%20parties%2C%20too%2C%20have%20turned%20against%20AAP%20for%20delay%20in%20action%20on%20this%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20Chandigarh%2C%20senior%20Akali%20Dal%20leaders%20Bikram%20Singh%20Majithia%20and%20Daljit%20Singh%20Cheema%20accused%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20acting%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Ctout%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20Haryana%20government%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20claimed%20that%20his%20failure%20to%20register%20a%20case%20against%20Haryana%20police%20personnel%20when%20they%20attacked%20farmers%20in%20Punjab%E2%80%99s%20territory%20on