that%20they%20were%20not%20as%20good%20Indians%20as%20any.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20intriguing%20speculation%20among%20Kshatriya%20Hindus%20that%20if%20the%20BJP%20secures%20a%20majority%2C%20Yogi%20Adityanath%2C%20who%20belongs%20to%20their%20community%2C%20may%20be%20ousted%20from%20his%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20never%20been%20a%20secret%20that%20there%20has%20never%20been%20any%20love%20lost%20between%20him%20and%20the%20Union%20home%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20reports%20from%20reliable%20journalists%20and%20knowledgeable%20social%20thinkers%2C%C2%A0if%20this%20speculation%20were%20to%20gain%20force%2C%C2%A0the%20Thakurs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Felections%2Futtar-pradesh%2Fyogi-a-major-factor-in-thakur-support-for-bjp-1073184.html%5C%22%3Emay%20turn%20on%20the%20ruling%20BJP%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20if%20only%20to%20ensure%20Yogi%E2%80%99s%20continuance%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20anticipated%20that%20Brahmins%20who%20have%20been%20feeling%20rather%20left%20out%20by%20the%20Yogi%20regime%20may%20split%2C%20and%20a%20sizable%20number%20may%C2%A0do%20a%20walk%20back%20to%20their%20old%20love%2C%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20to%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20it%20is%20more%20a%20myth%20than%20a%20reality%20that%20he%20has%20any%20hold%20among%20the%20Kurmis%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20reports%20suggest%20that%20deals%20between%20Kurmis%20and%20leaders%20of%20some%20%E2%80%98Extremely%20Backward%20Castes%E2%80%99%20with%20the%20BJP%20are%20still%20in%20the%20doldrums.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Congress%20and%20AAP%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-and-aap-seal-seat-sharing-deal-for-delhi-haryana-gujarat-goa-but-to-go-solo-in-punjab%5C%22%3Ehave%20announced%3C%2Fa%3E%20seat-sharing%20arrangements%20for%20Delhi%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20Goa%2C%20and%20Chandigarh%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%2