%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333558%2Fbest-farm-stays-in-india-with-natural-pool-organic-food-slow-travel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20homestay%3C%2Fa%3E%20is.%20Simplicity%20defines%20the%20essence%20of%20this%20homestay.%20While%20at%20first%20glance%2C%20you%20may%20be%20perplexed%20at%20how%20the%20family%20navigates%20life%20with%20the%20bare%20necessities%2C%20in%20the%20days%20that%20follow%2C%20it%20will%20be%20evident%20that%20nature%20is%20all%20you%20need%20to%20feel%20complete.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKundan%20has%20spent%20the%20better%20part%20of%20his%20life%20tending%20to%20his%20apple%20orchard%2C%20and%20so%2C%20every%20guest%20is%20treated%20to%20delicacies%20that%20feature%20that%20fruit.%20As%20he%20gives%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20a%20rundown%20of%20the%20neighbourhood%2C%20he%20says%20entertaining%20guests%20is%20his%20favourite%20thing%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%E2%80%99ll%20see%20this%20for%20yourself%20if%20you%20take%20a%20trip%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2030-minute%20bus%20ride%20from%20Kullu%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F321695%2Faamir-khanyari-turned-ancestral-land-into-traditional-kashmir-homestay%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecosy%20homestay%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20bone-rattling%20with%20the%20unwelcome%20terrain%20playing%20spoilsport.%20But%20once%20you%20reach%20Kundan%E2%80%99s%20home%2C%20all%20discomfort%20is%20washed%20away%20by%20the%20warm%20soup%2C%20prepared%20and%20served%20by%20his%20wife%20Kala%20as%20a%20welcome%20drink.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20smiling%20couple%20%E2%80%94%20who%20are%20in%20their%20forties%20%E2%80%94%20will%20unleash%20their%20hospitality%20upon%20your%20arrival.%20They%20will%20waste%20no%20time%20in%20telling%20you%20that%20this%20is%20your%20home%20and%20you%20must%20make%20yourself%20feel%20at%20ease.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECome%20evening%20and%20Kundan%20