.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FPearl-farming-4-1708610636-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FPearl-farming-4-1708610636-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FPearl-farming-4-1708610636-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-342940%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIn%20the%20last%20batch%2C%20Vinod%20managed%20to%20extract%2010%2C000%20pearls.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20first%20failure%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20his%20graduation%20in%20the%20arts%20field%2C%20Vinod%20pursued%20a%20diploma%20in%20computer%20science%20in%201999.%20Thereafter%2C%20he%20started%20working%20as%20a%20computer%20tutor%20in%20an%20institute%20and%20eventually%20opened%20his%20own%20academy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBack%20then%2C%20the%20computer%20was%20very%20new%20to%20people%20and%20they%20were%20interested%20in%20learning%20the%20new%20device.%20I%20would%20get%20students%20across%20all%20age%20groups.%20However%2C%20I%20was%20forced%20to%20shut%20down%20the%20institute%20after%20five%20years%20as%20I%20was%20not%20getting%20many%20students%20at%20the%20village%20level%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vinod.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithout%20any%20sustainable%20work%2C%20he%20would%20do%20odd%20jobs%20to%20earn%20a%20living.%20It%20was%20only%20in%202017%20that%20he%20understood%20what%20he%20was%20meant%20to%20do.%20%E2%80%9CBy%20that%20time%2C%20I%20was%20looking%20for%20ways%20where%20I%20could%20start%20a%20business%20with%20less%20capital%20and%20space.%20One%20day%2C%20one%20of%20my%20friends%20suggested%20I%20try%20my%20hands%20at%20oyster%20pearl%20farming%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20did%20not%20want%20to%20get%20into%20traditional%20farming%20as%20I%20had%20s