very%20similar.%20Both%20involve%20agricultural%20biomass%20being%20treated%20with%20microbes.%E2%80%9D%20Thus%20began%20the%20journey%20of%20Akshay%20and%20his%20mentor%20testing%20different%20kinds%20of%20microbes%20across%20farming%20lands%20for%20their%20characteristics%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20see%20which%20would%20work%20best%20when%20added%20to%20fertilisers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETowards%202020%2C%20Akshay%20had%20managed%20to%20come%20up%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F338548%2Fmaharashtra-farmer-earns-huge-profits-by-growing-strawberry-farm-near-pune%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20set%20of%20biofertilisers%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20were%20all%20performing%20well.%20That%20same%20year%2C%20he%20formally%20launched%20LCB%20Fertilizers%20Pvt%20Ltd.%20But%20just%20when%20things%20were%20looking%20up%2C%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20hit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20prepared%20microbe%20mixes%20in%20the%20laboratory%20and%20were%20in%20the%20process%20of%20testing%20the%20mixes%20on%20plants%20to%20check%20their%20efficiency.%20I%20had%20to%20return%20home%20with%20no%20idea%20of%20when%20I%20could%20get%20back%20to%20the%20lab.%20In%20the%20time%20that%20I%20was%20away%2C%20the%20microbe%20mixes%20had%20dried%20up%20and%20were%20now%20useless.%20I%20was%20back%20to%20square%20one%20%E2%80%94%20no%20lab%2C%20no%20money%20and%20no%20hope%20for%20what%20is%20next.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDisappointment%20at%20having%20been%20so%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F338048%2Fterrace-garden-tips-by-hyderabad-woman-grows-organic-vegetables-at-home%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclose%20to%20the%20dream%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20having%20to%20give%20up%2C%20clouded%20Akshay%E2%80%99s%20mind.%20During%20this%20time%20he%20was%20also%20offered%20a%20job%2C%20but%20a%20gut%20feeling%20told%20him%20he%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20give%20up%20on%20his%20dream%20just%20yet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%2C%20the%20next%20day%2C%20with%20a%20Rs%2010%2C000%20investment%2C%20Akshay%20decided%20to%20turn%20his%20shed%20outside%20his%20home%20into%20his%20lab.%20%E2%80%9CI%20purchased%20a%20pump%20from%20Amazon%2C%20a%20temperature%20sensor%20and%20I%20set%20up%20a%20bioreactor%20in%20my%20house.%20I%20had%20the%20know-how%20to%20prepare%20the%20fertiliser.%20I%20decided%20to%20do%20it%20at%20home.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20the%20weeks%20that%20followed%2C%20Akshay%20went%20around%20collecting%20old%20wood%2C%20and%20soil%20from%20different%20types%20of%20environments%20%E2%80%94%20from%20harsh%20climates%2C%20marshy%20areas%20to%20loamy%20soil%20and%20cow%20dung.%20The%20first%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F337129%2Feroponics-tower-planter-for-balcony-garden-by-iit-kanpur-startup-macrogardens%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebatch%20of%20fertiliser%3C%2Fa%3E%20he%20prepared%20weighed%203%20kg.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-9-1708604729.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Navyakosh%20fertiliser%20bridges%20the%20gap%20between%20chemical%20and%20organic%20fertilisers%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-9-1708604729.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-9-1708604729-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-9-1708604729-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-9-1708604729-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-9-1708604729-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-342917%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Navyakosh%20fertiliser%20bridges%20the%20gap%20between%20chemical%20and%20organic%20fertilisers%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Akshay%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-10-1708605146.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20first%20production%20unit%20started%20by%20LCB%20Fertilizers%2C%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-10-1708605146.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-10-1708605146-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-10-1708605146-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-10-1708605146-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-10-1708605146-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-342918%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20first%20production%20unit%20started%20by%20LCB%20Fertilizers%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Akshay%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkshay%20then%20proceeded%20to%20divide%20a%2012%20sq%20ft%20area%20outside%20the%20home%20into%20different%20portions.%20He%20planted%20seeds%20of%20carrots%2C%20spinach%20and%20radish%20in%20each%20portion%20but%20the%20choice%20of%20fertiliser%20was%20different%20%E2%80%94%20one%20batch%20was%20grown%20with%20a%20chemical%20fertiliser%2C%20one%20was%20grown%20with%20cow%20dung%2C%20one%20was%20grown%20with%20LCB%20fertiliser%20and%20the%20last%20with%20no%20fertiliser%20at%20all.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20you%20can%20guess%20which%20one%20thrived!%20Once%20the%20lockdown%20eased%20in%202021%2C%20Akshay%20approached%20IIT%20Kanpur%20where%20he%20met%20Dr%20Amitabha%20Bandopadhyay%20who%20helped%20him%20access%20labs%2C%20office%20space%2C%20and%20more.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20this%2C%20a%20NIDHI%20Prayas%20Grant%20from%20the%20Department%20of%20Science%20and%20Technology%2C%20along%20with%20financial%20support%20of%20around%20Rs%208%20lakh%2C%20also%20boosted%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F336832%2Fias-officer-sushant-gaurav-transforms-gumla-district-of-jharkhand-with-ragi-millet%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproduct%E2%80%99s%20development%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0Akshay%20was%20joined%20by%20Mukesh%20Singh%2C%20Shubhendra%20and%20Raj%20Kamal%20in%20his%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20so%20special%20about%20this%20fertiliser%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20why%20crops%20seem%20to%20be%20loving%20the%20LCB%20fertiliser%2C%20Akshay%20says%20it%20is%20because%20it%20provides%20them%20with%20everything%20they%20were%20missing%20in%20other%20chemical%20and%20organic%20fertilisers.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSimply%20put%2C%20the%20fertiliser%20has%20four%20components.%20The%20first%20is%20a%20combination%20of%20microbes%20%E2%80%94%20nitrogen-fixing%2C%20potassium-mobilising%2C%20phosphorus-solubilising%2C%20and%20Trichoderma.%20This%20set%20helps%20the%20plant%20access%20the%20nutrients%20that%20it%20needs%20to%20grow%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20component%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F336600%2Ftech-nursery-hydroponics-aeroponics-farming-ratlam-brothers-arbind-ravindra-dhakad%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eagricultural%20biomass%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20comprises%20seven%20types%20of%20biomass%20such%20as%20bagasse%2C%20cow%20dung%2C%20etc.%20The%20third%20component%20is%20the%20nanoparticles%20which%20increase%20the%20resistance%20of%20the%20microbes%20and%20help%20them%20survive%20in%20areas%20where%20it%20is%20hot.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20makes%20them%20thermophilic%20so%20that%20the%20microbes%20can%20survive%20at%20temperatures%20as%20high%20as%2070%20degrees%20celsius%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-11-1708605231.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Navyakosh%20fertiliser%20also%20helps%20farmers%20reduce%20the%20number%20of%20times%20they%20irrigate%20the%20land%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-11-1708605231.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-11-1708605231-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-11-1708605231-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-11-1708605231-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-11-1708605231-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-342919%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Navyakosh%20fertiliser%20also%20helps%20farmers%20reduce%20the%20number%20of%20times%20they%20irrigate%20the%20land%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Akshay%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-12_11zon-1708605899.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20health%20of%20crops%20has%20visibly%20increased%20after%20farmers%20used%20the%20Navyakosh%20fertilisers%2C%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-12_11zon-1708605899.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-12_11zon-1708605899-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-12_11zon-1708605899-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-12_11zon-1708605899-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-12_11zon-1708605899-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-342920%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20health%20of%20crops%20has%20visibly%20increased%20after%20farmers%20used%20the%20Navyakosh%20fertilisers%2C%20says%20Akshay%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Akshay%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20fourth%20component%20is%20a%20polymer%20which%20holds%20260%20times%20its%20weight%20in%20water%20and%20helps%20plants%20in%20drought-prone%20regions%2C%E2%80%9D%20Akshay%20adds.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20LCB%20fertiliser%20helps%20reduce%20the%20cost%20for%20a%20farmer%20(from%20Rs%206600%20for%20one%20acre%20to%20Rs%204000%20for%20an%20acre)%20while%20making%20the%20process%20hassle-free.%20Because%20of%20the%20polymer%2C%20farmers%20only%20have%20to%20irrigate%20the%20land%20once%20in%2025%20days%20in%20contrast%20to%20once%20in%2015%20days.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Akshay%20claims%20that%20over%2035%2C000%20farmers%20have%20benefitted%20from%20the%20product.%20As%20more%20and%20more%20farmers%20are%20adopting%20this%20new%20piece%20of%20wonder%2C%20Akshay%20says%20he%20feels%20it%20is%20a%20personal%20win.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20grown%20up%20watching%20what%20farmers%20have%20to%20endure%20because%20of%20products%20that%20do%20not%20perform%20well.%20I%E2%80%99m%20happy%20that%20I%20can%20help%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708610946000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D342901%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Akshay%20Shrivastav%2C%20a%20chemical%20engineer%2C%20launched%20'Navyakosh'%2C%20a%20unique%20fertiliser%20rich%20in%20microbes%20that%20can%20help%20farmers%20increase%20their%20productivity.%20He%20started%20his%20company%2C%20LCB%20Fertilizers%2C%20in%20his%20backyard%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic-induced%20lockdown.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98My%20Dad%E2%80%99s%20a%20Farmer%20%26amp%3B%20This%20Was%20a%20Dream%E2%80%99%3A%20Engineer%20Grows%20Rare%20%E2%80%98Yellow%20Dates%E2%80%99%2C%20Reaps%20Big%20Profits%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhile%20most%20of%20the%20youth%20in%20the%20country%20are%20heading%20towards%20corporate%20jobs%2C%20only%20a%20few%20turn%20towards%20farming.%20Affected%20by%20various%20factors%2C%20especially%20high%20risk%20and%20low%20profitability%2C%20no%20farmer%20would%20want%20his%20son%20to%20become%20a%20farmer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20know%20that%20there%20is%20a%20certain%20perspective%20towards%20taking%20up%20farming.%20But%20I%20was%20very%20sure%20from%20the%20beginning%20of%20my%20career%20that%20I%20would%20end%20up%20in%20the%20agriculture%20industry%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F342247%2Fmangaluru-man-quits-corporate-career-for-farming-exotic-fruits-vegetables-earns-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20engineer-turned-agriprenuer%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20Nagendra%20Naidu%20Dharmavarapu%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Farmties%20India%20Private%20Limited.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Nagendra%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20find%20one%E2%80%99s%20niche%20in%20farming%20to%20earn%20profits.%20He%20found%20his%20niche%20in%20Yellow%20Dates%2C%20a%20super%20food%2C%20which%20is%20earning%20him%20Rs%203.5%20lakhs%20per%20acre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIntrigued%20by%20the%20product%20and%20how%20he%20found%20his%20market%2C%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20had%20a%20conversation%20with%20Nagendra%20where%20he%20recalls%20his%20initial%20days%20of%20brainstorming%20to%20make%20profits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBack%20to%20his%20roots%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20into%20a%20family%20of%20farmers%2C%20Nagendra%20grew%20up%20in%20close%20proximity%20to%20the%20issues%20farmers%20faced%20on%20a%20daily%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20intimately%20familiar%20with%20these%20challenges%20and%20had%20grown%20up%20pondering%20potential%20solutions.%20In%20my%20mind%2C%20it%20was%20clear%20that%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20an%20agripreneur%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20while%20Nagendra%20was%20in%20an%20engineering%20college%2C%20he%20would%20frequently%20return%20home%20and%20spend%20time%20on%20the%20farm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20a%20strong%20affinity%20for%20the%20farms%20and%20was%20very%20determined%20that%20one%20day%20I%20would%20also%20transition%20into%20the%20agriculture%20space%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2F