.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20providing%20rations%20worth%20Rs%20600%20per%20child%20every%20month.%20This%20ration%20kit%20was%20expected%20to%20be%20provided%20once%20or%20twice%20a%20month.%20The%20additional%20ration%20support%20was%20given%20for%20three%20to%20six%20months%20to%20MAM%20%5Bmoderate%20acute%20malnutrition%5D%20kids%2C%20whereas%20nine%20to%2012%20months%20for%20SAM%20%5Bseverely%20acute%20malnutrition%5D%20children%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FKatni-1708432131.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20district%20is%20providing%20rations%20worth%20Rs%20600%20per%20child%20every%20month.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FKatni-1708432131.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FKatni-1708432131-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FKatni-1708432131-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FKatni-1708432131-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FKatni-1708432131-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-342448%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20district%20is%20providing%20rations%20worth%20Rs%20600%20per%20child%20every%20month.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20initiative%2C%20the%20IAS%20officer%20says%2C%20has%20brought%20people%20from%20all%20walks%20of%20life%20and%20groups%20%E2%80%94%20including%20industrialists%2C%20doctors%2C%20non-profit%20organisations%2C%20and%20individuals%20%E2%80%94%20to%20join%20the%20nutrition%20campaign%20of%20the%20district%20ad