%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ELilies%20need%20at%20least%20six%20hours%20of%20sunlight%20to%20thrive.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20They%20love%20the%20sun!%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EViji%20says%20that%20lilies%20love%20sunlight%20and%20they%20need%20sunlight.%20%E2%80%9CMake%20sure%20they%20get%20at%20least%20six%20hours%20of%20sunlight%20every%20day.%20This%20is%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20why%20many%20lily%20plants%20become%20dormant.%20Place%20your%20pots%20in%20a%20sunny%20place%20and%20see%20your%20lilies%20bloom%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Natural%20fertilisers%20can%20go%20a%20long%20way%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20providing%20the%20plants%20with%20sunlight%20and%20good%20soil%2C%20Viji%20recommends%20feeding%20them%20with%20natural%20fertilisers.%20%E2%80%9CVermicompost%20can%20do%20wonders%20for%20your%20lilies.%20You%20can%20also%20use%20cow%20dung%20to%20give%20more%20nutrients%20to%20the%20soil.%20While%20you%20might%20be%20tempted%20to%20use%20chemical%20fertilisers%2C%20there%20is%20no%20need.%20These%20locally%20sourced%2C%20natural%20ingredients%20can%20go%20a%20long%20way%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Find%20your%20gardening%20friends%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20advice%20is%20for%20all%20the%20new%20gardeners%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CDo%20not%20hesitate%20to%20connect%20with%20people%20and%20ask%20for%20help.%20The%20first%20time%20I%20tried%20my%20hand%20at%20growing%20water%20plants%2C%20it%20was%20a%20complete%20disaster.%20If%20I%20had%20not%20gone%20to%20Facebook%20groups%20and%20asked%20for%20help%2C%20I%20would%20not%20be%20here.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20chance%20that%20your%20first%20attempt%20might%20lead%20to%20dead%20plants%20or%20they%20might%20go%20dormant.%20There%20might%20be%20some%20losses%20but%20asking%20for%20help%20will%20always%20come%20as%20a%20relief%20to%20you.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20pictures%20credit%3A%20Viji)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708090665000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fflowers-5-1708088457.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D342126%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Viji%20Abi%2C%20a%20passionate%20gardener%20from%20Thrissur%2C%20Kerala%2C%20grows%20a%20variety%20of%20water%20lilies%2C%20earning%20over%20Rs%201%20lakh%20monthly.%20Learning%20from%20the%20International%20Waterlily%20and%20Water%20Gardening%20Society%2C%20she%20created%20a%20hybrid%20variety.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A192%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F342126%2Fhow-to-grow-water-lily-at-home-gardener-viji-abi-shares-easy-tips-thrissur-nymphaea-sree%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Lenovo%20Used%20Technology%20to%20Revive%20the%20Lost%20Millets%20of%20a%20Kerala%20Village%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20published%20in%20collaboration%20with%20Lenovo%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Kanthalloor%20Grama%20Panchayat%20President%20P%20T%20Mohandas%20was%20campaigning%20for%20elections%20in%202020%2C%20he%20saw%20huge%20sacks%20lying%20in%20several%20households.%20On%20inquiry%2C%20he%20found%20that%20each%20of%20the%20tribal%20households%20there%20had%20almost%20500%20to%201%2C000%20kg%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F329588%2Fentrepreneur-startup-green-energy-foundation-gud-mom-millet-products-help-organic-farmers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efinger%20millet%3C%2Fa%3E%20(%3Cem%3Eragi%3C%2Fem%3E)%20lying%20unused.%20Reason%20%E2%80%94%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20to%20sell%20it%20and%20used%20this%20superfood%20solely%20for%20self-consumption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESomething%20had%20to%20be%20done%2C%20thought%20Mohandas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20he%20began%20seeking%20ways%20to%20sell%20the%20surplus%20%3Cem%3Eragi%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20uplift%20the%20villagers%E2%80%99%20livelihoods%2C%20Lenovo%20was%20also%20exploring%20ways%20to%20integrate%20technology%20for%20farmers%E2%80%99%20welfare%20and%20promote%20the%20cultivation%20of%20millets%20in%20Kanthalloor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKanthalloor%20was%20once%20home%20to%20over%2018%20varieties%20of%20millet%2C%20according%20to%20farmers.%20But%20over%20the%20past%2020%20years%2C%20as%20people%20shifted%20towards%20consuming%20more%20rice%20and%20wheat%2C%20millet%20consumption%20gradually%20reduced%20and%20so%20did%20its%20cultivation.%20The%20village%20lost%20its%20diverse%20variety%20of%20millet%20and%20the%20number%20came%20down%20from%2018%20to%20just%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELenovo%20embarked%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20revive%20millet%20cultivation%20in%20the%20Idukki%20district%20and%20help%20farmers%20flourish%20through%20the%20assistance%20of%20technology.%20Through%20its%20%E2%80%98Work%20for%20Humankind%E2%80%99%20initiative%2C%20the%20volunteers%20have%20helped%20reinstate%20some%20lost%20millets%2C%20bringing%20the%20millet%20variety%20to%20six.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20it%20has%20set%20up%20a%20digital%20centre%2C%20worked%20on%20the%20branding%20and%20marketing%20of%20the%20millets%2C%20and%20set%20up%20a%20processing%20unit%20%E2%80%94%20all%20to%20help%20Kanthalloor%E2%80%99s%20farmers%20restore%20its%20generational%20millet%20glory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20about%201%2C800%20kg%20of%20six%20types%20of%20millet%20%E2%80%94%20including%20finger%20millet%2C%20barnyard%20millet%2C%20little%20millet%2C%20foxtail%20millet%2C%20proso%20millet%2C%20and%20kodo%20millet%20%E2%80%94%20have%20been%20cultivated%20by%2025%20farmers%20on%2015%20acres%20of%20land%20in%20the%20village.%20This%20harvest%20has%20also%20been%20processed%20and%20packaged%2C%20and%20will%20be%20sold%20through%20the%20various%20channels.%20The%20farmers%20hail%20this%20initiative%20and%20hope%20that%20it%20will%20be%20a%20harbinger%20of%20a%20better%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20human-centric%20innovation%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FLenovo1-1708067454.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Farmers%20were%20earlier%20growing%20millets%20only%20for%20self-consumption%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FLenovo1-1708067454.jpeg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FLenovo1-1708067454-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FLenovo1-1708067454-500x333.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FLenovo1-1708067454-768x512.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FLenovo1-1708067454-1536x1023.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FLenovo1-1708067454-150x100.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FLenovo1-1708067454-272x182.jpeg%20272w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-342035%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221066%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EFarmers%20were%20earlier%20growing%20millets%20only%20for%20self-consumption.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKanthalloor%2C%20a%20village%20surrounded%20by%20the%20Western%20Ghats%20in%20Kerala%E2%80%99s%20Idukki%20district%2C%20used%20to%20be%20a%20hub%20for%20millets%2C%20cultivating%20nearly%2018%20varieties%20until%20three%20decades%20ago.%20However%2C%20its%20proximity%20to%20the%20Chinnar%20Wildlife%20Sanctuary%20poses%20a%20challenge%20for%20farmers%20due%20to%20animals%20like%20boars%20and%20elephants%20damaging%20their%20millet%20crops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20consumerism%20grew%20and%20the%20sale%20of%20rice%20increased%2C%20the%20demand%20for%20millets%20declined.%20This%20too%20affected%20the%20tribal%20community%20living%20in%20the%20forest%2C%20lacking%20access%20to%20a%20proper%20market%20for%20their%20produce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20light%20of%202023%20being%20the%20%E2%80%98International%20Year%20of%20the%20Millet%E2%80%99%2C%20Lenovo%20aimed%20to%20revive%20this%20traditional%20superfood%20in%20Kanthalloor%2C%20as%20shared%20by%20Pratima%20Harite%2C%20Head%20of%20Asia%20Pacific%20CSR%20%26amp%3B%20Philanthropy%20at%20Lenovo%20Foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20an%20idea%20to%20mobilise%20the%20community%20using%20technology%2C%20Lenovo%20first%20surveyed%20227%20households%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3Egrama%20panchayat%3C%2Fem%3E.%20They%20found%20that%20over%2060%20percent%20of%20households%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332580%2Fmillet-based-startups-helping-farmers-ragi-jowar-international-year-of-millet%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecultivated%20millet%3C%2Fa%3E%20only%20in%20a%20small%20portion%20of%20their%20land%20i.e.%20below%2020%20cents.%20This%20was%20not%20the%20case%20earlier%2C%20according%20to%20Mohandas%2C%20who%20states%20that%20over%2060%20percent%20of%20the%20land%20was%20used%20to%20cultivate%20millets%20a%20few%20decades%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20to%20help%20these%20farmers%20go%20back%20to%20their%20roots%20and%20start%20cultivating%20millets%20again%2C%20this%20time%20empowered%20with%20the%20help%20of%20technology%2C%20training%20and%20marketing.%20We%20believe%20that%20smart%20technology%20solutions%20have%20the%20power%20to%20transform%20communities%20and%20revive%20lost%20traditions.%20This%20technology%20would%20also%20help%20the%20younger%20generation%20take%20the%20information%20forward%20in%20their%20families%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pratima%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELenovo%2C%20through%20its%20%E2%80%98Work%20for%20Humankind%E2%80%99%20initiative%20has%20partnered%20with%20Dream%20India%20Network%20%E2%80%94%20a%20non-profit%20organisation%20working%20on%20the%20ground%20%E2%80%94%20as%20the%20implementation%20partner%3B%20the%20Grama%20Panchayat%20for%20eco-tourism%20and%20farmer%20engagement%3B%20IHRD%20College%20for%20Applied%20Sciences%2C%20Kanthalloor%2C%20for%20setting%20up%20their%20technology%20centre%3B%20and%20Samudra%20Network%20and%20Agri%20app%20as%20their%20digital%20integration%20partner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20activity%20that%20Lenovo%20undertook%20with%20the%20help%20of%20Dream%20India%20Network%2C%20was%20to%20choose%2025%20farmers%20%E2%80%94%2016%20of%20whom%20are%20women%20%E2%80%94%20from%20five%20wards%20and%20convince%20them%20to%20sow%20millets%20in%20a%20portion%20of%20their%20land.%20They%20were%20given%20good-quality%20seeds%20and%20taught%20different%20ways%20to%20revive%20the%20crop.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20farmers%20were%20already%20growing%20%3Cem%3Eragi%20%3C%2Fem%3Efor%20self-consumption.%20We%20asked%20them%20to%20try%20growing%20any%20of%20the%20other%20five%20varieties%20in%2050%20cents%20of%20their%20unused%20land%20by%20instilling%20confidence%20that%20we%20would%20market%20it.%20Since%20the%20land%20was%20already%20used%20for%20millet%20cultivation%20earlier%2C%20there%20would%20be%20no%20problem.%20Furthermore%2C%20millets%20grow%20in%20low-fertility%20soils%20and%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20need%20too%20much%20water.%20They%20just%20need%20timely%20rain%20to%20get%20a%20good%20harves